  <para style="h">UJoshuwa</para>
  <para style="toc1">UJoshuwa</para>
  <para style="toc2">UJoshuwa</para>
  <para style="toc3">Josh</para>
  <para style="mt1">UJoshuwa</para>
  <para style="imt">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="imt1">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="im">Incwadi kaJoshuwa leyaBahluleli zikhuluma ngodaba lweminyaka yokusungulwa kwesizwe sako-Israyeli. Izincwadi lezi zichaza ukunqoba lokuthumba kwabo ilizwe laseKhenani lokutshikatshika kwabo ekugcineni isivumelwano sabo loNkulunkulu wabo. Udaba lweBhayibhili lapha luphothuluka lusiya esigabeni esiqakathekileyo lapho abantu bakaNkulunkulu beselizweni likaNkulunkulu. Lanxa kunjalo, kubasobala ukuthi indlela yokubuyisana koluntu loNkulunkulu izakuba nzima.</para>
  <para style="ip">Udaba luchaza amalungiselelo lezimpi zokuhlasela kwabako-Israyeli kanye lendlela izizwe zako-Israyeli ezazilehlukaniselane ngayo. Njengoba imvukela yala ikhona, uJoshuwa enkulumeni yakhe yokucina ukhuthaza ukuthi isizwe ngesizwe sithathe ngokupheleleyo isabelo selizwe esiqondene laso. Uqhubeka ngokuthungamela abantu ukuthi bavuselele ukuzinikela kwabo ekugcineni isivumelwano sabo loNkulunkulu.</para>
  <para style="ip">Incwadi yakhe (uJoshuwa) yaBahluleli ikhuluma ngokungalaleli lokuhlamuka kwabako-Israyeli ekwephuleni isivumelwano, bethunjwa ngezinye izizwe lokukhala kwabo kuNkulunkulu bedinga usizo. Kodwa ukusizakala kwabo ngokwesikhatshana nje, ngoba basuka babuyele ebubini babo njalo. (“Abahluleli” balinxusa lamabutho kanye labaphathi bomthetho.)</para>
  <para style="ip">Njengoba u-Israyeli wayebunjwe ngezizwe ezilitshumi lambili, lencwadi le isitshela ngabahluleli abalitshumi lambili. Kodwa njengoba abako-Israyeli beqhubeka ngezindlela zabo ezimbi sithola ukuthi sebedele Inkosi loMahluli wabo oqotho. Ngokwanda kobubi lobudlwangudlwangu kusuka kubaluleke ukuthi abako-Israyeli bayayidinga inkosi. Emaphethelweni kuvela imibuzo ethi: Kambe abako-Israyeli bangakuveza ukubizwa kwabo ngokuthi bayisibane sikaNkulunkulu ezizweni? Ngubani ongabusa u-Israyeli abancedise ekuvezeni umlandu wakhe kuloludaba lokusindiswa komhlaba?</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" sid="JOS 1"/>
  <para style="s1">
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> Ulaya UJoshuwa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 1:1"/>Ngemva kokufa kukaMosi inceku <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wathi kuJoshuwa indodana kaNuni, umsekeli kaMosi: <verse eid="JOS 1:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 1:2"/>“UMosi inceku yami usefile. Ngakho-ke, wena labantu bonke laba, lungiselelani ukuchapha umfula uJodani liye elizweni esengizalinika lona, abako-Israyeli. <verse eid="JOS 1:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 1:3"/>Ngizalinika zonke izindawo lapho elizanyathela khona ngezinyawo zenu njengokuthembisa engakwenza kuMosi. <verse eid="JOS 1:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 1:4"/>Ilizwe lenu lizasukela enkangala yeLebhanoni lasemfuleni omkhulu uYufrathe, ilizwe lonke lamaHithi, lize liyekhawula olwandle olukhulu entshonalanga. <verse eid="JOS 1:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 1:5"/>Kakulamuntu ozenelisa ukumelana lani zonke insuku zokuphila kwenu. Njengoba ngangiloMosi, ngizakuba lawe; kangisoze ngikutshiye, kangisoze ngikudele. <verse eid="JOS 1:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 1:6"/>Qina ube lesibindi ngenxa yokuthi uzakhokhela abantu laba ukuze bayethatha ilizwe elilifa labo engafunga kubokhokho babo ukuthi ngizabanika lona.<verse eid="JOS 1:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 1:7"/>Qina ube lesibindi. Ugcine yonke imithetho owayiphiwa nguMosi inceku yami, ungaze waphambuka kuyo uye kwesokunene kumbe kwesokhohlo ukuze uphumelele kuzozonke izindawo ozakuya kuzo. <verse eid="JOS 1:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 1:8"/>INcwadi yoMthetho le kayingasuki emlonyeni wakho, cabanga ngayo emini lebusuku ukuze unanzelele ukugcina konke okulotshwe kuyo. Ngokwena njalo uzaphumelela. <verse eid="JOS 1:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 1:9"/>Angikulayanga na? Qina ube lesibindi, ungethuki njalo ungalahli ithemba, ngoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wakho uzakuba lawe loba kungaphi lapho oya khona.”<verse eid="JOS 1:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 1:10"/>Ngakho-ke uJoshuwa walaya iziphathamandla zabantu wathi: <verse eid="JOS 1:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 1:11"/>“Dabulani phakathi kwezihonqo litshele abantu ukuthi, ‘Lungisani imiphako yenu. Ensukwini ezintathu kusukela lamhla lizachapha uJodani lapha ukuze lingene liyethatha ilizwe <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu alinika lona ukuba libe ngelenu!’ ”<verse eid="JOS 1:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 1:12"/>UJoshuwa wathi kwabakoRubheni, labakoGadi lengxenye yesizwana sikaManase, <verse eid="JOS 1:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 1:13"/>“Khumbulani umlayo uMosi inceku <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> alinika wona owokuthi: ‘<char style="nd">UThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu uzaliphumuza ngokulinika ilizwe leli.’ <verse eid="JOS 1:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 1:14"/>Amakhosikazi enu, abantwabenu lezifuyo zenu zingahlala elizweni elalinikwa nguMosi empumalanga yeJodani, kodwa ibutho lenu lonke, lihlome liphelele, kumele lichaphe ngaphambi kwabafowenu. Kuzamele lincedise abafowenu, <verse eid="JOS 1:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 1:15"/><char style="nd">uThixo</char> aze abaphumuze, njengalokho alenzele khona lina, labo baze bathathe ilizwe lelo <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu abanika lona. Ngemva kwalokho selingabuyela liyehlala elizweni lenu, uMosi inceku <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> alinika lona ngempumalanga yeJodani.”<verse eid="JOS 1:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOS 1:16"/>Baphendula uJoshuwa bathi, “Konke osilaya khona sizakwenza, lalapho osithuma khona sizahamba. <verse eid="JOS 1:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOS 1:17"/>Njengalokhu salalela uMosi ngokupheleleyo, lawe sizakulalela. Sifisa ukuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wakho abe lawe njengoba wayeloMosi. <verse eid="JOS 1:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOS 1:18"/>Yiloba ngubani ohlamukela ilizwi lakho njalo engalaleli lokho okutshoyo, lalokho oyabe ukulaya, kumele abulawe. Kumele uqine ube lesibindi!”<verse eid="JOS 1:18"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 1"/>
  <chapter number="2" style="c" sid="JOS 2"/>
  <para style="s1">URahabi Lezinhloli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 2:1"/>UJoshuwa indodana kaNuni wasethumela inhloli ezimbili ngasese zisuka eShithima. Wathi kuzo, “Hambani liyehlola ilizwe lakhona, ikakhulu iJerikho.” Ngakho zahamba zayangena endlini yesifebe esithiwa nguRahabi, zahlala khona.<verse eid="JOS 2:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 2:2"/>Inkosi yaseJerikho yatshelwa ukuthi “Khangela! Abanye abantu bako-Israyeli bafike lapha ebusuku ukuzohlola ilizwe lethu.” <verse eid="JOS 2:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 2:3"/>Ngakho inkosi yaseJerikho yathumela ilizwi kuRahabi yathi, “Khupha amadoda angene endlini yakho, ngoba alande ukuzohlola ilizwe lonke.”<verse eid="JOS 2:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 2:4"/>Kodwa owesifazane wayethethe amadoda womabili wawafihla. Wasesithi, “Liqiniso amadoda afikile kimi, kodwa bengingazi ukuthi abevela ngaphi. <verse eid="JOS 2:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 2:5"/>Kusihlwa, sesifikile isikhathi sokuvala isango ledolobho, amadoda asuke azihambela. Kangikwazi ukuthi aqonde ngaphi. Axhumeni masinyane. Engxenye lingawafica.” <verse eid="JOS 2:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 2:6"/>(Kodwa wayebakhweze phezu kophahla wabafihla ngaphansi kwezinqwaba zesikusha ayesichaye ophahleni). <verse eid="JOS 2:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 2:7"/>Ngakho amadoda aphuma ijumo elandela inhloli emgwaqweni oya ezibukweni leJodani, njalo athi esanda kuphuma isango lavalwa.<verse eid="JOS 2:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 2:8"/>Inhloli zathi zingakalali ngalobobusuku, wakhwela phezu kophahla <verse eid="JOS 2:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 2:9"/>wasesithi kuzo, “Ngiyazi ukuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uselinike lelilizwe lokuthi sonke sesehlelwe yikwesaba okukhulu ngenxa yenu, okwenza ukuthi bonke abahlala kulelilizwe babelomhedehede wokulesaba. <verse eid="JOS 2:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 2:10"/>Sesizwile ukuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> walenzela amanzi oLwandle Olubomvu atsha ngesikhathi liphuma eGibhithe, lalokho elakwenza kuSihoni lo-Ogi amakhosi amabili ama-Amori empumalanga yeJodani elawatshaya lawaqothula. <verse eid="JOS 2:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 2:11"/>Sathi sikuzwa lokho inhliziyo zethu zahle zaphela amandla njalo wonke umuntu kazabe esaba lesibindi ngenxa yenu ngoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu unguNkulunkulu ophezulu ezulwini laphansi emhlabeni.<verse eid="JOS 2:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 2:12"/>Ngakho-ke ngicela ukuthi lifunge kimi <char style="nd">ngoThixo</char> ukuthi lizakuba lomusa emulini yami ngoba lami ngitshengise umusa kini. <verse eid="JOS 2:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 2:13"/>Nginikani isiqiniseko sokuthi lizaphephisa impilo kababa lomama, abanewethu labodadewethu labo bonke abangababo, njalo lizasisindisa ekufeni.”<verse eid="JOS 2:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 2:14"/>Amadoda amthembisa athi, “Ukuphila kwethu yikuphila kwenu! Ungayekela ukuveza lokho esikwenzayo sizakwenzela umusa lokwethembeka lapho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> esesipha ilizwe.”<verse eid="JOS 2:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 2:15"/>Ngakho-ke wabehlisela phansi ngentambo baphuma ngefasitela kalokho indlu ayehlala kuyo yayingumduli munye lalowo owawugombolozele idolobho. <verse eid="JOS 2:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOS 2:16"/>Wayethe kubo, “Qondani emaqaqeni ukwenzela ukuthi abaxhuma umzila wenu bangaze balifica. Licatshe khonale okwensuku ezintathu baze baphenduke beseliqhubeka ngendlela yenu.”<verse eid="JOS 2:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOS 2:17"/>Amadoda athi kuye, “Isifungo osifungise sona sizakuba yize <verse eid="JOS 2:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOS 2:18"/>ngaphandle kokuthi nxa sesingena kulelilizwe sifice ubophele leliqhele elibomvu ewindini osikhuphe ngalo, njalo usulethe uyihlo lonyoko, abafowenu lemuli yakho yonke endlini yakho. <verse eid="JOS 2:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOS 2:19"/>Nxa umuntu angaphuma phandle kwendlu yakho abesesiya esitaladeni, igazi lakhe lizakuba sekhanda lakhe: kawusoze ube ngumlandu wethu. Kuye wonke oyabe ephakathi kwendlu kanye lawe, igazi lakhe lizakuba sekhanda lethu nxa angavele athintwe. <verse eid="JOS 2:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOS 2:20"/>Kodwa ungavele uveze lokhu esikwenzayo, sizabe sesikhululiwe esifungweni osifungise sona.”<verse eid="JOS 2:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOS 2:21"/>Waphendula wathi, “Ngiyavuma, kakube njengokutsho kwenu.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="JOS 2:21">Ngakho wavalelisana labo basebezihambela. Wasebophela iqhele elibomvu ewindini.<verse eid="JOS 2:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOS 2:22"/>Bathi besuka lapho baqonda emaqaqeni lapho abahlala khona okwensuku ezintathu ababebaxhuma baze badela ukubadinga emgwaqweni wonke, basebebuyela bengababonanga. <verse eid="JOS 2:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOS 2:23"/>Ngakho-ke amadoda womabili aphindela emuva. Ehla emaqaqeni, achapha umfula, afika kuJoshuwa indodana kaNuni amtshela konke okwakwenzakele kuwo. <verse eid="JOS 2:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOS 2:24"/>Athi kuJoshuwa, “<char style="nd">UThixo</char> ngeqiniso uphe ilizwe lonke ezandleni zethu; bonke abantu bayathuthumela ngokwesaba, ngenxa yethu.”<verse eid="JOS 2:24"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 2"/>
  <chapter number="3" style="c" sid="JOS 3"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukuchapha UJodani</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 3:1"/>Ekuseni kakhulu uJoshuwa labo bonke abako-Israyeli basuka eShithima baqonda eJodani lapho abamisa khona izihonqo zabo bengakachaphi. <verse eid="JOS 3:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 3:2"/>Ngemva kwensuku ezintathu iziphathamandla zangena phakathi kwezihonqo, <verse eid="JOS 3:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 3:3"/>zinika imilayo ebantwini zisithi, “Lapho libona umtshokotsho wesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu labaphristi abangabaLevi belithwele kuzamele litshiye izindawo zenu lililandele. <verse eid="JOS 3:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 3:4"/>Ngakho lizakwazi ukuthi lilandele yiphi indlela, njengoba lingakaze libe kuwonalo umango. Kodwa kumele ligcine ibanga elingaba yizingalo eziyinkulungwane ezimbili phakathi kwenu lomtshokotsho; lingasondeli phansi kwalo.”<verse eid="JOS 3:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 3:5"/>UJoshuwa wathi ebantwini, “Zihlambululeni ngoba kusasa <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uzakwenza izimanga phakathi kwenu.”<verse eid="JOS 3:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 3:6"/>UJoshuwa wathi kubaphristi, “Thathani umtshokotsho wesivumelwano beselikhokhela phambi kwabantu.” Ngakho bawuthatha basebehamba phambi kwabo.<verse eid="JOS 3:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 3:7"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuJoshuwa, “Lamhla ngizaqalisa ukukuphakamisa emehlweni abako-Israyeli bonke ukuze babone ukuthi ngilawe njengoba ngangiloMosi. <verse eid="JOS 3:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 3:8"/>Tshela abaphristi abathwala umtshokotsho wesivumelwano uthi, ‘Lingafika okhunjini lwamanzi kaJodani, lingene liyekuma phakathi komfula.’ ”<verse eid="JOS 3:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 3:9"/>UJoshuwa wathi kwabako-Israyeli, “Wozani lapha lizolalela amazwi <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu. <verse eid="JOS 3:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 3:10"/>Lokhu yikho okuzakwenza ukuthi lazi ukuthi uNkulunkulu ophilayo uphakathi kwenu njalo ngempela uzaxotsha phambi kwenu amaKhenani, amaHithi, amaHivi, amaPherizi, amaGigashi, ama-Amori lamaJebusi. <verse eid="JOS 3:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 3:11"/>Khangelani, umtshokotsho wesivumelwano seNkosi womhlaba wonke lizangena phakathi kweJodani phambi kwenu. <verse eid="JOS 3:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 3:12"/>Ngakho-ke, khethani amadoda alitshumi lambili esuka ezizwaneni zako-Israyeli, oyedwa esizwaneni esisodwa. <verse eid="JOS 3:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 3:13"/>Kuzakuthi masinyazana abaphristi abathwele umtshokotsho <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>, iNkosi yomhlaba wonke, sebengene eJodani, amanzi omfula ogelezayo azakwehlukaniswa abesesima abe yinqwaba.”<verse eid="JOS 3:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 3:14"/>Ngakho kwathi abantu sebesuke ezihonqweni ukuze bayechapha uJodani, abaphristi ababethwele umtshokotsho wesivumelwano bahamba phambili. <verse eid="JOS 3:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 3:15"/>UJodani wayehlala egcwele ngezikhathi zonke zokuvuna. Kukanti kwathi abaphristi ababethwele umtshokotsho befika eJodani inyawo zabo zazithinta amanzi, <verse eid="JOS 3:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOS 3:16"/>amanzi ayevelela ngaphezulu ema ukugeleza. Abuthana aba yinqwaba ema khatshana laphaya, malungana ledolobho elithiwa yi-Adamu duzane leZarethani kukanti amanzi ayegelezela phansi ngekuyeni olwandle lwe-Arabha (okutsho uLwandle Lwetswayi) ahle ehlukaniswa ngokupheleleyo. Ngakho-ke abantu bachaphela ngaphetsheya malungana leJerikho. <verse eid="JOS 3:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOS 3:17"/>Abaphristi ababethwele umtshokotsho wesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> bema bathi mpo emhlabathini owomileyo phakathi kweJodani, ngesikhathi abantu bonke bako-Israyeli bechapha isizwe sonke saze saqeda ukuchapha emhlabathini owomileyo.<verse eid="JOS 3:17"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 3"/>
  <chapter number="4" style="c" sid="JOS 4"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 4:1"/>Kwathi isizwe sonke sesimchaphile uJodani, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wathi kuJoshuwa, <verse eid="JOS 4:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 4:2"/>“Khetha amadoda alitshumi lambili phakathi kwabantu, yileyo imele isizwana sako-Israyeli, <verse eid="JOS 4:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 4:3"/>ubusubatshela ukuthi bathathe amatshe alitshumi lambili phakathi laphakathi kweJodani kusukela lapho okwakumi khona abaphristi, beseliwathwala liwabeke endaweni elizalala kuyo lamuhla ebusuku.”<verse eid="JOS 4:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 4:4"/>Ngakho-ke uJoshuwa wabiza amadoda alitshumi lambili ayewakhethe phakathi kwabako-Israyeli, eyodwa ivela esizwaneni. <verse eid="JOS 4:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 4:5"/>Wasesithi kuwo, “Hambani phambi komtshokotsho wesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu liye phakathi laphakathi kweJodani. Omunye lomunye wenu kumele athwale ilitshe ehlombe lakhe, kusiya ngenani lezizwana zako-Israyeli, <verse eid="JOS 4:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 4:6"/>ukuze kube luphawu phakathi kwenu. Kwelizayo nxa abantwana benu belibuza besithi, ‘Kanti amatshe la atshoni?’ <verse eid="JOS 4:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 4:7"/>Libatshele ukuthi ukugeleza kweJodani kwamiswa phambi komtshokotsho wesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char>. Kwathi lapho umtshokotsho uchapha iJodani, amanzi omfula uJodani ehlukaniswa. Amatshe la azakuba yisukhumbuzo ebantwini bako-Israyeli nini lanini.”<verse eid="JOS 4:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 4:8"/>Ngakho-ke abako-Israyeli benza njengokulaya kukaJoshuwa. Bathatha amatshe alitshumi lambili phakathi laphakathi kweJodani, kusiya ngenani lezizwana zako-Israyeli, njengokulaywa kukaJoshuwa <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>; basebewathwalela ezihonqweni zabo lapho abafika bawabeka khona phansi. <verse eid="JOS 4:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 4:9"/>UJoshuwa wamisa amatshe alitshumi lambili ayekade ephakathi laphakathi kweJodani, endaweni lapho abaphristi ababethwele umtshokotsho wesivumelwano abafika bema khona njalo lokhu ekhonapho kuze kube lamhlanje.<verse eid="JOS 4:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 4:10"/>Abaphristi ababethwele umtshokotsho baqhubeka bemi phakathi kweJodani abantu baze baqeda konke <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ayekulaye uJoshuwa, njengokuqondiswa kukaJoshuwa nguMosi. Abantu bedlula ngokuphangisa <verse eid="JOS 4:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 4:11"/>njalo bathi bonke sebechaphile, umtshokotsho wesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> labaphristi beza kwelinye icele abantu bekhangele. <verse eid="JOS 4:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 4:12"/>Amadoda akoRubheni, akoGadi lengxenye yesizwana sakoManase achapha ehlomile phambi kwabako-Israyeli njengokuqondisa kukaMosi. <verse eid="JOS 4:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 4:13"/>Abantu abaphose bafike kunkulungwane ezingamatshumi amane ababehlomele impi bachapha phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> besiya emagcekeni eJerikho ukuyakulwa impi.<verse eid="JOS 4:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 4:14"/>Ngalelolanga <char style="nd">uThixo</char> waphakamisa uJoshuwa emehlweni abo bonke abako-Israyeli; njalo bamhlonipha okwempilo yakhe yonke, njengoba babehloniphe uMosi.<verse eid="JOS 4:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 4:15"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuJoshuwa, <verse eid="JOS 4:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOS 4:16"/>“Laya abaphristi abathwele umtshokotsho woBufakazi bakhuphuke baphume eJodani.”<verse eid="JOS 4:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOS 4:17"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa walaya abaphristi wathi, “Phumani phakathi kweJodani.”<verse eid="JOS 4:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOS 4:18"/>Abaphristi baphuma emfuleni bethwele umtshokotsho wesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char>. Bonela ukunyathela umhlabathi owomileyo amanzi eJodani ahle abuyela endaweni yawo, ageleza okomfula ogcweleyo njengakuqala.<verse eid="JOS 4:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOS 4:19"/>Ngelanga letshumi enyangeni yakuqala abantu basuka eJodani bayamisa izihonqo eGiligali emngceleni ongempumalanga yeJerikho. <verse eid="JOS 4:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOS 4:20"/>UJoshuwa wamisa amatshe alitshumi ayethethwe phakathi kweJodani eGiligali. <verse eid="JOS 4:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOS 4:21"/>Wakhuluma kwabako-Israyeli wathi, “Kwelizayo nxa izizukulwane zenu zingabuza abazali bazo zisithi, ‘Amatshe la atshoni?’ <verse eid="JOS 4:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOS 4:22"/>Kumele libatshele ukuthi ‘Abako-Israyeli bachapha uJodani emhlabathini owomileyo!’ <verse eid="JOS 4:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOS 4:23"/>Ngoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu womisa umfula uJodani phambi kwenu laze lachapha. <char style="nd">UThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu wenza kuJodani lokho akwenza oLwandle Olubomvu aze alomise phambi kwethu saze sachapha sonke. <verse eid="JOS 4:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOS 4:24"/>Wenza lokhu ukuze abantu bonke bomhlaba bakwazi ukuthi isandla <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> silamandla lokuthi lihlale limesaba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu.”<verse eid="JOS 4:24"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 4"/>
  <chapter number="5" style="c" sid="JOS 5"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 5:1"/>Kwathi amakhosi ama-Amori ayebusa entshonalanga kweJodani lamakhosi wonke amaKhenani ayebusa ezigcawini ezisekela ulwandle esizwa ukuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wayomise njani uJodani phambi kwabako-Israyeli baze bachapha, inhliziyo zawo zathuthumela aswela izibindi zokumelana labako-Israyeli.<verse eid="JOS 5:1"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukusokwa LePhasika EGiligali</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 5:2"/>Ngalesosikhathi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wathi kuJoshuwa, “Khanda izingqamu ezibukhali ubususoka abako-Israyeli njalo.” <verse eid="JOS 5:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 5:3"/>Ngakho-ke uJoshuwa wakhanda izingqamu ezibukhali wasesoka abako-Israyeli eGibhiya Haralothi.<verse eid="JOS 5:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 5:4"/>Lokhu wakwenzela ukuthi: Bonke labo abaphuma eGibhithe, wonke amadoda ayengabuthelwa empini afela enkangala esemangweni wokusuka eGibhithe. <verse eid="JOS 5:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 5:5"/>Bonke abantu abaphumayo babesokiwe, kodwa bonke abantu ababezalelwe enkangala phakathi kohambo lokusuka eGibhithe babengasokwanga. <verse eid="JOS 5:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 5:6"/>Abako-Israyeli babezulazule enkangala okweminyaka engamatshumi amane, amadoda wonke ayefanele ukubuthelwa empini ngesikhathi esuka eGibhithe aze afa, njengoba engazange amlalele <char style="nd">uThixo</char>. Ngoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wayefunge waqinisa kubo wathi ayengasoze alibone ilizwe ayelithembise okhokho babo ukuthi bazalinikwa, ilizwe eligeleza uchago loluju. <verse eid="JOS 5:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 5:7"/>Ngakho wondla amadodana ezikhundleni zawo, njalo yiwo la asokwa nguJoshuwa. Ayelokhu engakasokwa ngoba kungazange kube lethuba lokubasoka endleleni. <verse eid="JOS 5:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 5:8"/>Kwathi isizwe sonke sesisokiwe, sahlala ezihonqweni baze baphola.<verse eid="JOS 5:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 5:9"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuJoshuwa, “Lamuhla ngisuse ihlazo laseGibhithe kini.” Yikho indawo leyo lokhu ibizwa ngokuthi yiGiligali kuze kube lamhlanje.<verse eid="JOS 5:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 5:10"/>Kusihlwa ngelanga letshumi lane kuleyo nyanga, bathi belokhu besamise izihonqo zabo eGiligali emagcekeni eJerikho, abako-Israyeli bagcina iPhasika. <verse eid="JOS 5:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 5:11"/>Ngokusa olwalandela usuku lwePhasika badla okunye kwesivuno sabo ababekuvunile: isinkwa esingelamvubelo lamabele akhanzingiweyo. <verse eid="JOS 5:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 5:12"/>Imana yema ukukhithika ngelanga elalandela lelo abadla ngalo ukudla okwakuvela emhlabathini; ngakho kwakungasela mana yabako-Israyeli, kodwa ngalowomnyaka badla okwelizwe leKhenani.<verse eid="JOS 5:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuwa KweJerikho</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 5:13"/>Kwathi uJoshuwa esesondele eJerikho, wakhangela wabona indoda eyayimi phambi kwakhe ilomhedla esandleni sayo, uJoshuwa wasondela kuyo wayibuza wathi “Ungowakithi kumbe ungowezitha zethu?”<verse eid="JOS 5:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 5:14"/>Yaphendula yathi “Angikho ndawo, kodwa njengomlawuli webutho <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> sengifikile.” UJoshuwa wathi mbo phansi ngobuso edumisa waseyibuza esithi, “Kambe iNkosi yami ilombiko bani wenceku yayo?”<verse eid="JOS 5:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 5:15"/>Umlawuli wamabutho <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> waphendula wathi, “Khulula izicathulo zakho ngoba indawo omi kuyo ingcwele.” UJoshuwa wenza njalo.<verse eid="JOS 5:15"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 5"/>
  <chapter number="6" style="c" sid="JOS 6"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 6:1"/>IJerikho yayivalwe ngci ngenxa yabako-Israyeli. Akulamuntu owayephuma loba owayengena.<verse eid="JOS 6:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 6:2"/>Ngakho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wathi kuJoshuwa, “Khangela, senginikele iJerikho, inkosi yayo kanye lamabutho ayo ezandleni zakho. <verse eid="JOS 6:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 6:3"/>Hambani libhode idolobho kanye lamadoda wonke ahlomileyo. Kwenzeni lokhu okwensuku eziyisithupha. <verse eid="JOS 6:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 6:4"/>Abaphristi abayisikhombisa kabathwale amacilongo enziwe ngempondo zenqama phambi komtshokotsho wesivumelwano. Ngosuku lwesikhombisa libhode idolobho kasikhombisa, abaphristi bevuthela amacilongo. <verse eid="JOS 6:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 6:5"/>Nxa lingabezwa sebetshaya amacilongo bedonsa, abantu bonke kabahlabe umkhosi; umduli wedolobho uzadilika abantu bahle bangene, yilowo lalowo aqonde phambili.”<verse eid="JOS 6:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 6:6"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa indodana kaNuni wabiza abaphristi wathi kubo, “Thathani umtshokotsho wesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> kuthi abaphristi abayisikhombisa bahambe phambi kwawo bethwele amacilongo.” <verse eid="JOS 6:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 6:7"/>Waselaya abantu esithi, “Akuhanjwe! Hambani libhode idolobho, amabutho ahlomileyo ehamba phambi komtshokotsho wesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char>.”<verse eid="JOS 6:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 6:8"/>Kwathi uJoshuwa esekhulume labantu, abaphristi abayisikhombisa ababethwele amacilongo ayisikhombisa phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> bahamba phambili bevuthela amacilongo, njalo umtshokotsho wesivumelwano ubalandela. <verse eid="JOS 6:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 6:9"/>Amabutho ayehlomile ahamba phambi kwabaphristi ababevuthela amacilongo, njalo amabutho angemuva ayelandela umtshokotsho. Ngasosonke lesisikhathi amacilongo ayekhala. <verse eid="JOS 6:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 6:10"/>Kodwa uJoshuwa wayelaye abantu wathi, “Lingaze lahlaba umkhosi wempini, lingakhwezi amazwi enu, lingakhulumi lutho kuze kufike isikhathi engizalitshela ngaso ukuthi limemeze. Beselihlaba-ke umkhosi.” <verse eid="JOS 6:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 6:11"/>Ngakho umtshokotsho wesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> bawuthwala babhoda lawo idolobho kanye. Abantu babuyela ezihonqweni bayalala.<verse eid="JOS 6:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 6:12"/>UJoshuwa wavuka kusesele ngelanga elilandelayo njalo abaphristi bathwala umtshokotsho wesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char>. <verse eid="JOS 6:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 6:13"/>Abaphristi abayisikhombisa ababethwele amacilongo ayisikhombisa bahamba phambili bekhokhele umtshokotsho wesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char>, bevuthela amacilongo. Amadoda ayehlomile ayehamba phambi kwabo njalo amabutho angemuva ayelandela umtshokotsho wesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char>, kukanti-ke amacilongo aqhubeka ekhala. <verse eid="JOS 6:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 6:14"/>Ngosuku lwesibili babhoda idolobho kanye basebebuyela ezihonqweni. Bakwenza lokhu okwensuku eziyisithupha.<verse eid="JOS 6:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 6:15"/>Ngelanga lesikhombisa bavuka emadabukakusa babhoda idolobho kasikhombisa ngendlela efanayo, ngaphandle kokuthi ngalelolanga babhoda kasikhombisa. <verse eid="JOS 6:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOS 6:16"/>Ngokwesikhombisa, kwathi abaphristi bekhalisa amacilongo, uJoshuwa walaya abantu wathi, “Memezani! Ngoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> useliphile idolobho. <verse eid="JOS 6:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOS 6:17"/>Idolobho lakho konke okukulo kuzakwahlukaniselwa <char style="nd">uThixo</char>. URahabi isifebe lalabo ahlala labo endlini yakhe yibo abazasindiswa ngenxa yokuthi wafihla inhloli esazithumayo. <verse eid="JOS 6:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOS 6:18"/>Kodwa xwayani izinto ezahlukaniselwe ukubhujiswa, ukwenzela ukuthi lingazehliseli ukubhujiswa ngokuthatha okunye kwalezozinto. Lokho kungenza ukuthi izihonqo zako-Israyeli zehlelwe luhlupho njalo zitshabalaliswe. <verse eid="JOS 6:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOS 6:19"/>Sonke isiliva, igolide lezinto zonke ezenziwe ngethusi langensimbi ezingcwele ziletheni <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> njalo kumele zifakwe esiphaleni sakhe sengcebo.”<verse eid="JOS 6:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOS 6:20"/>Kwathi amacilongo ekhala abantu bahlaba umkhosi; ekukhaleni kwecilongo, abantu sebehlaba umkhosi omkhulu, umduli wabhidlika, ngakho wonke umuntu wangena phakathi balithatha idolobho. <verse eid="JOS 6:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOS 6:21"/>Idolobho balehlukanisela <char style="nd">uThixo</char> basebecakaza ngenkemba yonke into ephilayo eyayihlala kulo, amadoda labesifazane, abatsha labadala, inkomo, izimvu labobabhemi.<verse eid="JOS 6:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOS 6:22"/>UJoshuwa wakhuluma emadodeni amabili ayeke athunywa njengezinhloli zelizwe wathi, “Yanini endlini yesifebe liyesikhupha lezihlobo zaso zonke ligcwalise isifungo elasenza kuso.” <verse eid="JOS 6:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOS 6:23"/>Ngakho amadoda ayahambe ukuyahlola angena akhupha uRahabi, uyise lonina labanewabo lazozonke izihlobo zakhe. Bakhupha imuli yonke bayifaka endaweni eyayingaphandle kwezihonqo zako-Israyeli.<verse eid="JOS 6:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOS 6:24"/>Basebetshisa idolobho lonke lakho konke okwakuphakathi kwalo, kodwa befake isiliva legolide lezinto ezilungiswe ngethusi lensimbi esiphaleni sengcebo yendlu <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>. <verse eid="JOS 6:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOS 6:25"/>Kodwa uJoshuwa waphephisa uRahabi isifebe lemuli yakhe labo bonke abangabakhe ngenxa yokuthi wafihla amadoda ayethunywe nguJoshuwa ukuba zinhloli eJerikho, futhi ulokhu ehlala phakathi kwabako-Israyeli kuze kube lamhlanje.<verse eid="JOS 6:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOS 6:26"/>Ngalesosikhathi uJoshuwa wenza isifungo esiqinileyo esithi, “Iqalekisiwe phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> indoda ezimisela ukwakha kutsha lelidolobho laseJerikho:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOS 6:26">Ngempilo yezibulo lakhe lendodana</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOS 6:26">uzakwenza izisekelo;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOS 6:26">ngempilo yecinathunjana</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOS 6:26">uzalungisa amasango alo.”<verse eid="JOS 6:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOS 6:27"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wayeloJoshuwa, udumo lwakhe lwanda elizweni lonke.<verse eid="JOS 6:27"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 6"/>
  <chapter number="7" style="c" sid="JOS 7"/>
  <para style="s1">Isono Sika-Akhani</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 7:1"/>Kodwa abako-Israyeli bephula umthetho ngokuphathelane lengcebo eyayehlukaniselwe <char style="nd">uThixo</char>; u-Akhani indodana kaKhami, indodana kaZabhidi, indodana kaZera, owesizwana sakoJuda, wathatha ezinye zakhona. Ngakho ulaka <char style="nd">lukaThixo</char> lwavutha kwabako-Israyeli.<verse eid="JOS 7:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 7:2"/>UJoshuwa wasethumela amadoda esuka eJerikho esiya e-Ayi eseduzane leBhethi-Aveni ngempumalanga yeBhetheli wathi kubo: “Hambani liyehlola lelolizwe.” Ngakho amadoda aphuma ayalihlola ilizwe.<verse eid="JOS 7:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 7:3"/>Bathi bephindela kuJoshuwa bafika bathi, “Akudingeki ukuthi lonke ibutho liyelwisana le-Ayi. Thumela amadoda azinkulungwane ezimbili kumbe ezintathu nje ukuze ayoyithumba njalo ungaze wadinisa ibutho lonke, ngenxa yokuthi lelodolobho lilabantu abalutshwana.” <verse eid="JOS 7:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 7:4"/>Amadoda angaba zinkulungwane ezintathu asuka ahamba kodwa ehlulwa ngamadoda e-Ayi, wona <verse eid="JOS 7:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 7:5"/>abulala amadoda angamatshumi amathathu lesithupha. Baxotsha abako-Israyeli besuka esangweni ledolobho baze bayabatshiya enkwalini bababulalela ekwehleni. Bathi besizwa lokhu abantu baba lokwesaba okukhulu, baphelelwa ngamandla.<verse eid="JOS 7:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 7:6"/>UJoshuwa wadabula izigqoko zakhe wathi mbo phansi ngobuso phambi komtshokotsho wesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char>, wala elokhu enjalo kwaze kwahlwa. Abadala bako-Israyeli labo benza njalo, basebezithela ngothuli emakhanda abo. <verse eid="JOS 7:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 7:7"/>UJoshuwa wasesithi, “Maye, <char style="nd">Thixo</char> Wobukhosi, wabachaphiselani iJodani lababantu ukuzabanikela ezandleni zama-Amori ukuze asibhubhise? Ngabe sasuthiseka ngokuzihlalela kwelinye iphetsheya leJodani! <verse eid="JOS 7:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 7:8"/>Maye, Thixo kuyini engingakutsho, njengoba u-Israyeli esebhuqwe yizitha zakhe? <verse eid="JOS 7:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 7:9"/>AmaKhenani labanye abantu belizwe bazakuzwa ngalokhu besebesihanqa besule ibizo lethu emhlabeni. Pho kuyini ozakwenzela ibizo lakho elikhulu kangaka na?”<verse eid="JOS 7:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 7:10"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuJoshuwa, “Sukuma. Kuyini okwenzayo uthe mbo ngobuso bakho? <verse eid="JOS 7:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 7:11"/>Abako-Israyeli bonile; bephule isivumelwano sami engabalaya ukuthi basigcine. Sebethethe ezinye izinto ezahlukaniselwe mina; bebile, baqamba amanga, sebezifake empangweni yabo. <verse eid="JOS 7:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 7:12"/>Yikho abako-Israyeli bengeke bamelana lezitha zabo; bayabafulathela bebaleka ngoba sebeyinto efanele ukubhujiswa. Kangisoze ngibe lani ngaphandle kokuthi lichithe lokho okwakwehlukaniselwe ukubhujiswa.<verse eid="JOS 7:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 7:13"/>Hamba ungcwelise abantu. Ubatshele uthi, ‘Zingcweliseni ukulungiselela kusasa; ngoba lokhu yikho okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu wako-Israyeli ukuthi: Lokho okwahlukaniselwe <char style="nd">uThixo</char> kuphakathi kwenu, lina bako-Israyeli. Kalingeke limelane lezitha zenu ngaphandle kokuba selikukhuphile.<verse eid="JOS 7:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 7:14"/>Ekuseni kumele lisondeze isizwana ngesizwana. Isizwana esikhethwa <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> kuzamele sisondele phambili usendo ngosendo; usendo oluzakhethwa <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> luzasondela imuli ngemuli; imuli ezakhethwa <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> izasondela umuntu ngamunye. <verse eid="JOS 7:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 7:15"/>Lowo ozafunyanwa elezinto ezahlukaniselwe <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uzatshiswa ngomlilo, lakho konke alakho. Wephule isivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> njalo wenze into elihlazo phakathi kuka-Israyeli.’ ”<verse eid="JOS 7:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOS 7:16"/>Kusesele ngelanga elilandelayo uJoshuwa wenza u-Israyeli wasondela ngezizwana, inkatho yadla koJuda. <verse eid="JOS 7:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOS 7:17"/>Insendo zakoJuda zasondela, inkatho yadla abakoZera. Wasondeza insendo zakoZera ngezimuli. Inkatho yadla uZabhidi. <verse eid="JOS 7:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOS 7:18"/>UJoshuwa wasondeza imuli kaZabhidi indoda yinye ngayinye, inkatho yadla u-Akhani indodana kaKhami, indodana kaZabhidi, indodana kaZera owesizwana sakoJuda.<verse eid="JOS 7:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOS 7:19"/>UJoshuwa wathi ku-Akhani, “Ndodana yami, dumisa <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu ka-Israyeli, umuphe udumo. Ngitshela lokho okwenzileyo, ungaze wangifihlela.”<verse eid="JOS 7:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOS 7:20"/>U-Akhani waphendula wathi, “Liqiniso! Ngonile phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu wako-Israyeli. Nanku engikwenzileyo: <verse eid="JOS 7:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOS 7:21"/>Ngathi ngibona phakathi kwempango ingubo enhle yaseBhabhiloni, lamashekeli esiliva angamakhulu amabili lomgqala wegolide olesisindo samashekeli angamatshumi amahlanu ngakuhawukela, ngakuthatha. Ngakumbela phansi ethenteni lami, isiliva singaphansi.”<verse eid="JOS 7:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOS 7:22"/>UJoshuwa wathuma izithunywa, zagijima zaya ethenteni lakhe, zakufumana kufihlilwe ethenteni lakhe, isiliva singaphansi. <verse eid="JOS 7:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOS 7:23"/>Bathatha izinto ezazisethenteni, baziletha kuJoshuwa lebantwini bonke bako-Israyeli, bazichaya phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>.<verse eid="JOS 7:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOS 7:24"/>UJoshuwa labo bonke abako-Israyeli bathatha u-Akhani indodana kaZera lesiliva, ingubo, lomgqala wegolide, lamadodana lamadodakazi akhe, lenkomo zakhe, obabhemi kanye lezimvu, ithente lakhe lakho konke ayelakho bakusa esiHotsheni se-Akhori. <verse eid="JOS 7:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOS 7:25"/>UJoshuwa wathi, “Kungani usilethele uhlupho olungaka? <char style="nd">UThixo</char> uzakwehlisela uhlupho lamhlanje.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="JOS 7:25">Bonke abako-Israyeli bamkhanda ngamatshe, njalo bathi sebeqedile ukukhanda labanye ngamatshe babatshisa. <verse eid="JOS 7:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOS 7:26"/>Babuthelela inqwaba yamatshe amakhulu phezu kuka-Akhani alokhu ekhona lalamhlanje. Ukuvutha kolaka <char style="nd">lukaThixo</char> kwahle kwaphela. Ngakho leyondawo lalamhlanje ilokhu isabizwa ngokuthi yisiGodi sika-Akhori.<verse eid="JOS 7:26"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 7"/>
  <chapter number="8" style="c" sid="JOS 8"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukutshabalaliswa Kwe-Ayi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 8:1"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuJoshuwa, “Ungesabi, ungalahli ithemba. Thatha ibutho lonke uhambe uyehlasela i-Ayi, ngoba senginikele inkosi yase-Ayi, abantu bayo, idolobho layo lelizwe layo ezandleni zakho. <verse eid="JOS 8:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 8:2"/>Khonale uzakwenza owakwenza eJerikho lenkosini yakhona, kodwa lingazithathela impahla zonke eliyabe lizithumbile lezifuyo kube ngokwenu. Cathamani ngemva kwedolobho.”<verse eid="JOS 8:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 8:3"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa lebutho lonke baphuma bayahlasela i-Ayi. Wakhetha amabutho azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amathathu ayezingcitshi ukwedlula amanye ekulweni, wasewathuma ebusuku. <verse eid="JOS 8:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 8:4"/>Wawalaya wathi, “Lalelisisani, kumele licathame ngemva kwedolobho. Lingaze laya khatshana lalo. Lonke kumele lihlale liqaphele. <verse eid="JOS 8:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 8:5"/>Mina lalabo engizabe ngilabo sizaqhubeka siqonde edolobheni, kuthi nxa amadoda ephuma ukusihlasela njengalokho akwenza kuqala, sizawabalekela. <verse eid="JOS 8:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 8:6"/>Bazaxotshana lathi size sibahugele khatshana ledolobho, ngoba bazakuthi, ‘Bayasibalekela njengalokhu abakwenza kuqala.’ Ngakho nxa sesibabalekela, <verse eid="JOS 8:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 8:7"/>lina lizavuka lapho eliyabe licathame khona beselithumba idolobho. <char style="nd">UThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu uzalinikela ezandleni zenu. <verse eid="JOS 8:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 8:8"/>Nxa selilithumbile idolobho, lithungeleni ngomlilo. Yenzani lokho okulaywe <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>. Wobani leqiniso lokuthi lilandela iziqondiso zami.”<verse eid="JOS 8:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 8:9"/>UJoshuwa wasebalaya ukuthi bahambe, basebesiya endaweni okwakumele bacathame kuyo phakathi kweBhetheli le-Ayi, entshonalanga ye-Ayi kodwa uJoshuwa waqeda ubusuku lobo elabantu.<verse eid="JOS 8:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 8:10"/>Ekuseni ngelanga elilandelayo uJoshuwa waqoqa amabutho akhe, kwathi yena labadala bako-Israyeli bahamba phambi kwabo besiya e-Ayi. <verse eid="JOS 8:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 8:11"/>Iviyo lonke lalabo ayelabo lahamba laya edolobheni lafika lema phambi kwabo. Bamisa izihonqo enyakatho ye-Ayi, isigodi siphakathi kwabo ledolobho. <verse eid="JOS 8:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 8:12"/>UJoshuwa wayethethe amadoda aphosa afike kunkulungwane ezinhlanu wawacathamisa phakathi kweBhetheli le-Ayi entshonalanga yedolobho. <verse eid="JOS 8:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 8:13"/>Benza ukuthi amabutho aye ezikhundleni zawo zonke ezaziphakathi kwezihonqo enyakatho yedolobho lendaweni yokucathamela eyayisentshonalanga yalo. Ngalobobusuku uJoshuwa waya esigodini.<verse eid="JOS 8:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 8:14"/>Inkosi yase-Ayi yathi ibona lokhu yona lawo wonke amadoda akulelodolobho aphanga aphuma kusesele ekuseni ukuze ayehlangana lo-Israyeli empini kweyinye indawo ekhangelane le-Arabha. Kodwa yayingazi ukuthi kwakulamabutho ayeyicathamele ngemva kwedolobho. <verse eid="JOS 8:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 8:15"/>UJoshuwa labantu bonke bako-Israyeli bathambela ukubuyiselwa emuva, babalekela enkangala. <verse eid="JOS 8:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOS 8:16"/>Wonke amadoda e-Ayi atshelwa ukuthi abaxotshe, basebexotshana loJoshuwa badonselwa khatshana ledolobho. <verse eid="JOS 8:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOS 8:17"/>Kakukho lendoda eyodwa eyasala e-Ayi kumbe eBhetheli engazanga ixotshane labako-Israyeli.<verse eid="JOS 8:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOS 8:18"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuJoshuwa, “Phakamisa umkhonto osesandleni ukhombe e-Ayi, ngenxa yokuthi idolobho leli ngizalinikela ezandleni zakho.” Ngakho uJoshuwa wakhombela e-Ayi ngomkhonto wakhe. <verse eid="JOS 8:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOS 8:19"/>Wathi esanda kwenza lokhu, amadoda ayecathamele ukuhlasela aphakama masinyane ezindaweni ayekuzo agijimela phambili. Angena edolobheni alithumba, aphanga alithungela ngomlilo.<verse eid="JOS 8:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOS 8:20"/>Amadoda e-Ayi anyemukula abona intuthu eyayisuka edolobheni iqonga emayezini kodwa aswela ukuthi azabalekela ngaphi ngoba abako-Israyeli ababebalekele enkangala basebephendukele labo ababebaxotsha. <verse eid="JOS 8:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOS 8:21"/>Kwathi uJoshuwa labako-Israyeli bonke bebona ukuthi labo ababecatheme basebethumbe idolobho lokuthi intuthu yayiqonga emayezini ivela edolobheni, batshibilika baqalisa ukuhlasela amadoda ase-Ayi. <verse eid="JOS 8:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOS 8:22"/>Amadoda ayecatheme lawo aphuma edolobheni abahlasela, okwenza ukuthi babe phakathi laphakathi, inxa zombili zilabako-Israyeli. Abako-Israyeli babatshaya bababhuqa akwaze kwasala muntu owaphunyukayo. <verse eid="JOS 8:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOS 8:23"/>Kodwa bathatha inkosi yase-Ayi iphila basebeyiletha kuJoshuwa.<verse eid="JOS 8:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOS 8:24"/>Kwathi abako-Israyeli sebeqedile ukubulala wonke amadoda ase-Ayi emagcekeni enkangala lapho ababewaxotshele khona, njalo wonke esegwazwe ngenkemba, bonke abako-Israyeli babuyela e-Ayi babulala abantu bonke abakulelo dolobho. <verse eid="JOS 8:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOS 8:25"/>Amadoda labesifazane abazinkulungwane ezilitshumi lambili bafa ngalelolanga, bonke kungabantu be-Ayi, <verse eid="JOS 8:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOS 8:26"/>ngoba uJoshuwa kazange ehlise isandla sakhe esiphethe umkhonto ngawo baze babhujiswa bonke abantu ababehlala e-Ayi. <verse eid="JOS 8:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOS 8:27"/>Kodwa abako-Israyeli bathatha zonke izifuyo lempango yonke eyayithunjwe kulelodolobho njengokulaywa kukaJoshuwa <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>.<verse eid="JOS 8:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOS 8:28"/>UJoshuwa watshisa i-Ayi wayenza yaba lunxiwa oluyinqwaba, indawo engelakuhlalwa muntu kuze kube lamhlanje. <verse eid="JOS 8:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOS 8:29"/>Walengisa inkosi yase-Ayi esigodweni wayitshiya kwaze kwaba ntambama. Ekutshoneni kwelanga uJoshuwa walaya ukuthi bethule isidumbu sayo basiphosele esangweni ledolobho. Babuthelela inqumbi yamatshe phezu kwaso, njalo lokhu kunjalo kuze kube lamhlanje.<verse eid="JOS 8:29"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuvuselelwa Kwesivumelwano ENtabeni Yase-Ebhali</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="JOS 8:30"/>UJoshuwa wasesakhela <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu wako-Israyeli i-alithari e-Ebhali. <verse eid="JOS 8:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="JOS 8:31"/>Njengokulaya okwenziwa nguMosi inceku <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> kwabako-Israyeli, walakha njengokulaywa okulotshwe eNcwadini yoMthetho kaMosi i-alithari lamatshe angabazwanga, okungazanga kusetshenziswe nsimbi phezu kwawo. Kulo banikela <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> iminikelo yokutshiswa leminikelo yokuthula. <verse eid="JOS 8:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="JOS 8:32"/>Lapho, phambi kwabako-Israyeli uJoshuwa waloba ematsheni umthetho kaMosi ayewubhalile. <verse eid="JOS 8:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="JOS 8:33"/>Bonke abako-Israyeli, abezizweni labayinzalo yalelolizwe, labadala babo, iziphathamandla labahluleli babemi emaceleni womabili omtshokotsho wesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> bekhangelane lalabo ababelithwele, abaphristi, ababengabaLevi. Ingxenye yabantu yema phambi kwentaba yeGerizimu kwathi eyinye ingxenye yema phambi kwentaba ye-Ebhali, njengokulaya kukaMosi inceku <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> owayelaye ukuthi kubusiswe abantu bako-Israyeli.<verse eid="JOS 8:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="JOS 8:34"/>Emva kwalokho uJoshuwa wafunda wonke amazwi omthetho, izibusiso leziqalekiso, njengokulotshwa okwenziwe eNcwadini yeMithetho. <verse eid="JOS 8:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="JOS 8:35"/>Kakulalizwi elalaywa nguMosi elingazanga lifundwe nguJoshuwa phambi kombuthano wonke wako-Israyeli kugoqela abesifazane labantwana labezizweni ababehlala phakathi kwabo.<verse eid="JOS 8:35"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 8"/>
  <chapter number="9" style="c" sid="JOS 9"/>
  <para style="s1">Ubuqili BamaGibhiyoni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 9:1"/>Kwathi amakhosi wonke ayebusa ngentshonalanga yeJodani, layeselizweni lamaqaqa, layesewatheni lwamaqaqa angentshonalanga, layesekele uLwandle oLukhulu kusiyafika eLebhanoni, amakhosi amaHithi, ama-Amori, amaKhenani, amaPherizi, amaHivi lamaJebusi esizwa ngalezizinto <verse eid="JOS 9:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 9:2"/>ahlangana ukuze alwisane uJoshuwa labako-Israyeli.<verse eid="JOS 9:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 9:3"/>Kodwa kwathi ngesikhathi abantu beGibhiyoni sebezwe konke uJoshuwa ayekwenze eJerikho le-Ayi, <verse eid="JOS 9:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 9:4"/>benza ubuqili: Bahamba njengamanxusa ayelabobabhemi ababethwele amasaka adabukileyo lezigxingi zewayini ezindala ezazidabuke zangcinwa. <verse eid="JOS 9:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 9:5"/>Amadoda ayegqoke amanyathela ayedabukile njalo exaxelwe, begqoke lezigqoko ezigugileyo. Zonke izinkwa ababezithwele njengomphako zazomile njalo zikhuntile. <verse eid="JOS 9:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 9:6"/>Baya kuJoshuwa esihonqweni seGiligali bathi kuye lakwabako-Israyeli, “Sivela elizweni elikude; ngakho yenzani isivumelwano lathi.”<verse eid="JOS 9:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 9:7"/>Abako-Israyeli baphendula amaHivi bathi, “Kodwa mhlawumbe lihlala eduzane lathi, pho singasenza kanjani isivumelwano lani?”<verse eid="JOS 9:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 9:8"/>Bathi kuJoshuwa “Siyizinceku zenu.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="JOS 9:8">Kodwa uJoshuwa wababuza wathi, “Lingobani njalo livela ngaphi?”<verse eid="JOS 9:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 9:9"/>Baphendula bathi, “Izinceku zakho zivela elizweni elikude njalo zikhangwe yindumela <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu. Ngoba sesezwa imibiko eminengi ngaye: konke akwenza eGibhithe, <verse eid="JOS 9:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 9:10"/>lakho konke akwenza emakhosini amabili ama-Amori empumalanga yeJodani, uSihoni inkosi yeHeshibhoni lo-Ogi inkosi yaseBhashani owayebusa e-Ashitharothi. <verse eid="JOS 9:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 9:11"/>Abadala bethu labo bonke abakhileyo elizweni lakithi bathi kithi, ‘Thwalani umphako wohambo lwenu; lihambe liyehlangana labo lithi kubo, “Sizinceku zenu: yenzani isivumelwano lathi.” ’ <verse eid="JOS 9:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 9:12"/>Isinkwa sethu lesi sasifudumala ngesikhathi sisifaka emigodleni yethu sisesemakhaya ngelanga esasuka ngalo sisiza kini. Kodwa-ke khangelani ukuthi sesome njalo sakhunta njani. <verse eid="JOS 9:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 9:13"/>Izigxingi lezi zewayini esazigcwalisisayo zazizintsha, kodwa-ke khangelani ukuthi sezidabuke njani. Izigqoko lamanyathela ethu sekudatshulwe yibude bomango.”<verse eid="JOS 9:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 9:14"/>Abako-Israyeli bahlola imiphako yabo kodwa-ke kabasabuzanga <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>. <verse eid="JOS 9:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 9:15"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa wenza isivumelwano sokuthula labo wabavumela ukuthi bahlale, njalo abathungameli bebandla bavumelana lalokhu ngesifungo.<verse eid="JOS 9:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOS 9:16"/>Sekwedlule insuku ezintathu benze isivumelwano lamaGibhiyoni, abako-Israyeli bezwa ukuthi lababantu babengomakhelwana, ababehlala eduzane labo. <verse eid="JOS 9:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOS 9:17"/>Abako-Israyeli baya emadolobheni abo ayebalisa iGibhiyoni, iKhefira, iBherothi leKhiriyathi-Jeyarimi. <verse eid="JOS 9:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOS 9:18"/>Kodwa abako-Israyeli kabazange babahlasele ngenxa yokuthi abathungameli bebandla babefunge <char style="nd">ngoThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu wako-Israyeli.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="JOS 9:18">Ibandla lonke lakhonona ngabadala bebandla; <verse eid="JOS 9:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOS 9:19"/>kodwa bona bonke baphendula bathi, “Sibanike isifungo sethu <char style="nd">ngoThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu wako-Israyeli njalo asingeke sabathinta khathesi. <verse eid="JOS 9:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOS 9:20"/>Lokhu yikho esizakwenza kubo: Sizabayekela bahlale, ukuze ulaka lungezi kithi ngenxa yokwephula isifungo esasenza phambi kwabo.” <verse eid="JOS 9:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOS 9:21"/>Baqhubeka bathi, “Bayekeleni bahlale, kodwa bazakuba ngababandi benkuni labakhi bamanzi abazasebenzela uzulu wonke.” Ngakho-ke isivumelwano sabakhokheli sagcinwa.<verse eid="JOS 9:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOS 9:22"/>UJoshuwa wabiza wonke amaGibhiyoni wathi kuwo, “Kungani lisikhohlisile ngokuthi, ‘Sihlala khatshana lani, lina lihlala eduzane lathi kangaka?’ <verse eid="JOS 9:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOS 9:23"/>Seliqalekisiwe: kalisoze liyekele ukuba ngababandi benkuni labakhi bamanzi lisebenzela indlu kaNkulunkulu wami.”<verse eid="JOS 9:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOS 9:24"/>Baphendula uJoshuwa bathi, “Izinceku zakho zatshelwa mgceke ukuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu walaya njani inceku yakhe uMosi ukuthi alinike ilizwe lonke lokuthi litshabalalise bonke ababakhele kulo lina lingakafiki. Ngakho-ke sesabela impilo zethu ngenxa yenu, yikho okwenze senza lokhu. <verse eid="JOS 9:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOS 9:25"/>Sesizinikele ezandleni zenu. Yenzani kithi konke elikubona kufanele njalo kuqondile kini.”<verse eid="JOS 9:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOS 9:26"/>Ngakho-ke uJoshuwa wabasindisa esandleni sika-Israyeli, njalo kabasababulalanga. <verse eid="JOS 9:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOS 9:27"/>Ngalelolanga wenza ukuthi amaGibhiyoni abe ngababandi benkuni labakhi bamanzi besebenzela uzulu njalo besebenza e-alithareni <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> endaweni eyayikhethwe <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>. Yikho abayikhona kuze kube lamhlanje.<verse eid="JOS 9:27"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 9"/>
  <chapter number="10" style="c" sid="JOS 10"/>
  <para style="s1">Ilanga Lima Mpo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 10:1"/>U-Adoni-Zedekhi inkosi yaseJerusalema wezwa ukuthi uJoshuwa wayesethumbe i-Ayi wayitshabalalisa, njengalokho akwenza eJerikho lenkosini yayo, lokuthi abantu baseGibhiyoni babenze isivumelwano sokuthula labako-Israyeli njalo sebehlala labo. <verse eid="JOS 10:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 10:2"/>Yena labantu bakhe besaba kakhulu ngalokhu, ngenxa yokuthi iGibhiyoni kwakulidolobho eliqakatheke kakhulu, njengelinye lamadolobho esikhosini; lalilikhulu kule-Ayi, njalo amadoda alo wonke ayezingwazi ezilamandla. <verse eid="JOS 10:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 10:3"/>Ngakho u-Adoni-Zedekhi inkosi yaseJerusalema wakhalaza kuHohamu inkosi yaseHebhroni, kuPhiramu inkosi yaseJamuthi, kuJafiya inkosi yaseLakhishi lakuDebhiri inkosi yase-Egiloni. <verse eid="JOS 10:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 10:4"/>Wathi kubo, “Wozani lizongincedisa ukuhlasela iGibhiyoni ngenxa yokuthi yenze isivumelwano sokuthula loJoshuwa labako-Israyeli.”<verse eid="JOS 10:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 10:5"/>Ngakho amakhosi womahlanu ama-Amori, aseJerusalema, eHebhroni, eJamuthi, eLakhishi lase-Egiloni abambana. Aphuma lamabutho awo wonke ayihonqolozela iGibhiyoni ayihlasela.<verse eid="JOS 10:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 10:6"/>AmaGibhiyoni athumela ilizwi kuJoshuwa ezihonqweni zaseGiligali athi: “Ungalahli izinceku zakho. Woza ngapha kithi ngokuphangisa uzosisiza! Sincede, ngoba wonke amakhosi ama-Amori abusa emazweni asemaqaqeni asebambene ukuze alwisane lathi.”<verse eid="JOS 10:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 10:7"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa wasuka eGiligali, wenyuka kanye lebutho lakhe lonke, elaligoqela wonke amadoda ayekwazi ukulwa. <verse eid="JOS 10:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 10:8"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuJoshuwa, “Ungabesabi; sengibanikele esandleni sakho. Kakho loyedwa ozakwenelisa ukumelana lawe.”<verse eid="JOS 10:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 10:9"/>Ngemva kokuhamba okobusuku bonke besuka eGiligali, uJoshuwa wabajuma. <verse eid="JOS 10:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 10:10"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> wenza ukuthi basanganiseke phambi kuka-Israyeli, wabehlula ngokunqoba okukhulu eGibhiyoni. Abako-Israyeli baxotshana labo emgwaqweni oya eBhethi-Horoni, baxhumana labo baze bayafika e-Azekha leMakheda. <verse eid="JOS 10:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 10:11"/>Lapho bebalekela abako-Israyeli emgwaqweni osuka eBhethi-Horoni usiya e-Azekha, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wehlisa isiqhotho esikhulu sivela emkhathini, njalo inengi labo lafa libulawa yisiqhotho ukwedlula ababulawa zinkemba zabako-Israyeli.<verse eid="JOS 10:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 10:12"/>Ngalelolanga <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wanikela ngalo ama-Amori kwabako-Israyeli, uJoshuwa wathi <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> phambi kwabako-Israyeli:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="JOS 10:12">“We langa, mana uthi mpo ngaphezu kweGibhiyoni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOS 10:12">lawe nyanga, mana ngaphezu kweSigodi se-Ayijaloni.”<verse eid="JOS 10:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 10:13"/>Ngakho ilanga lema lathi mpo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOS 10:13">lenyanga yema,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOS 10:13">isizwe saze saphindisela ngokupheleleyo ezitheni zaso,</para>
  <para style="m" vid="JOS 10:13">njengoba kulotshiwe oGwalweni lukaJasha.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="JOS 10:13">Ilanga lema phakathi laphakathi kwesibhakabhaka laphuza ukutshona okosuku lonke. <verse eid="JOS 10:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 10:14"/>Kakuzange kube losuku olwafana lalo ngaphambili kumbe kuze kube lamhlanje, usuku lapho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> alalela khona umuntu. Ngeqiniso <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wayelwela u-Israyeli!<verse eid="JOS 10:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 10:15"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa waphindela labo bonke abako-Israyeli ezihonqweni zaseGiligali.<verse eid="JOS 10:15"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubulawa Kwamakhosi Amahlanu Ama-Amori</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOS 10:16"/>Amakhosi lawo womahlanu abaleka ayacatsha ebhalwini lwaseMakheda. <verse eid="JOS 10:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOS 10:17"/>Kwathi uJoshuwa esetshelwe ukuthi amakhosi womahlanu ayetholakale ecatshile ebhalwini lweMakheda, <verse eid="JOS 10:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOS 10:18"/>wathi, “Giqani amatshe amakhulu liwafake emlonyeni wobhalu, beselisithi amanye amadoda alinde. <verse eid="JOS 10:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOS 10:19"/>Kodwa lingemi! Xotshani izitha zenu, lingazivumeli ukuthi zifike emadolobheni azo, ngoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu esezinikele ezandleni zenu.”<verse eid="JOS 10:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOS 10:20"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa labako-Israyeli bababhubhisa baphosa baphela bonke kodwa abalutshwana abasalayo banelisa ukufika emadolobheni abo ayezinqaba. <verse eid="JOS 10:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOS 10:21"/>Ibutho lonke lenelisa ukuphenduka ngokuthula kuJoshuwa esihonqweni seMakheda, njalo kakho owake wakhuluma okubi ngabako-Israyeli.<verse eid="JOS 10:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOS 10:22"/>UJoshuwa wathi, “Vulani umlomo wobhalu beseliletha amakhosi womahlanu eze kimi.” <verse eid="JOS 10:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOS 10:23"/>Ngakho bakhupha amakhosi womahlanu ebhalwini, inkosi yaseJerusalema, eyeHebhroni, yeJamuthi, eyeLakhishi kanye leyase-Egiloni. <verse eid="JOS 10:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOS 10:24"/>Bathi sebelethe amakhosi la kuJoshuwa, wabiza wonke amadoda ako-Israyeli wasesithi kubo bonke abalawuli bamabutho ababeze laye, “Wozani lapha lizofaka inyawo zenu entanyeni zala amakhosi.” Ngakho beza phambili basebefaka inyawo zabo entanyeni zawo.<verse eid="JOS 10:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOS 10:25"/>UJoshuwa wathi kubo, “Lingesabi; lingadangali qinani libe lezibindi. Lokhu yikho okuzakwenziwa <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> kuzozonke izitha elizalwisana lazo.” <verse eid="JOS 10:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOS 10:26"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa wawabulala amakhosi la wawalengisa ensikeni ezinhlanu, alenga lapho kwaze kwahlwa.<verse eid="JOS 10:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOS 10:27"/>Ekutshoneni kwelanga uJoshuwa walaya ukuthi bawethule bawaphose ebhalwini lapho ayekade ecatshe khona. Emlonyeni wobhalu bafaka amatshe amakhulu alokhu ekhona lanamhlanje.<verse eid="JOS 10:27"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukunqotshwa Kwamadolobho Aseningizimu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOS 10:28"/>Ngalelolanga uJoshuwa wathumba iMakheda. Wahlasela idolobho kanye lenkosi yalo ngenkemba, wabhubhisa wonke umuntu owayephakathi kwalo. Kakho owatshiywa ephila. Wenza enkosini yeMakheda lokho ayekwenze enkosini yaseJerikho.<verse eid="JOS 10:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOS 10:29"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa labo bonke abako-Israyeli ababelaye basuka eMakheda baya eLibhina balihlasela. <verse eid="JOS 10:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="JOS 10:30"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> waphinda wanikela lelodolobho lenkosi yalo esandleni sika-Israyeli. UJoshuwa wahlasela ngenkemba idolobho laye wonke umuntu owayephakathi kwalo. Kakho owatshiywa ephila lapho. Wenza enkosini yalo lokho ayekwenze enkosini yeJerikho.<verse eid="JOS 10:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="JOS 10:31"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa labo bonke abako-Israyeli ayelabo bahamba besuka eLibhina besiya eLakhishi; balihanqa basebelihlasela. <verse eid="JOS 10:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="JOS 10:32"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> wanikela iLakhishi ku-Israyeli, uJoshuwa wayithatha ngelanga lesibili. Idolobho laye wonke umuntu owayephakathi kwalo wakuhlasela ngenkemba, njengalokho ayekwenze eLibhina. <verse eid="JOS 10:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="JOS 10:33"/>Kunjalo-nje uHoramu inkosi yaseGezeri yayize ukuzoncedisa iLakhishi kodwa uJoshuwa wayehlula ndawonye lebutho layo, kakho owatshiywa ephila.<verse eid="JOS 10:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="JOS 10:34"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa labo bonke abako-Israyeli ababelaye basuka eLakhishi baya edolobheni le-Egiloni; basebelihanqa balihlasela. <verse eid="JOS 10:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="JOS 10:35"/>Balithumba ngalelolanga, balihlakaza ngenkemba basebebhubhisa wonke umuntu owayephakathi kwalo, njengalokho ababekwenze eLakhishi.<verse eid="JOS 10:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="JOS 10:36"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa labo bonke abako-Israyeli ababelaye bahamba besuka e-Egiloni baya eHebhroni bayihlasela. <verse eid="JOS 10:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="JOS 10:37"/>Balithumba lelodolobho ngenkemba ndawonye lamakhosi alo, imizana yalo laye wonke umuntu owayephakathi kwalo, kakho owatshiywa ephila. Njengalokho abakwenza e-Egiloni, balitshabalalisa laye wonke umuntu owayephakathi kwalo.<verse eid="JOS 10:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="JOS 10:38"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa labo bonke abako-Israyeli ayelabo baphenduka bahlasela iDebhiri. <verse eid="JOS 10:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="JOS 10:39"/>Bathumba lelidolobho, inkosi lemizi yalo, bayihlasela ngenkemba. Bonke abantu ababephakathi kwalo babhujiswa baphela. Kakho owatshiywa ephila. Benza eDebhiri lenkosini yakhona lokho abakwenza eLibhina lenkosini yakhona kanye leHebhroni.<verse eid="JOS 10:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="JOS 10:40"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa wasinqoba sonke isabelo, okugoqela ilizwe lamaqaqa, iNegebi, emawatheni ezintaba entshonalanga lemithezukweni yezintaba ndawonye lamakhosi alapho wonke. Kakho owatshiywa ephila. Wabhubhisa bonke abebephefumula, njengoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu ka-Israyeli wayebalayile. <verse eid="JOS 10:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="JOS 10:41"/>UJoshuwa wabanqoba kusukela eKhadeshi Bhaneya kusiya eGaza lakuso sonke isabelo seGosheni kusiya eGibhiyoni. <verse eid="JOS 10:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="JOS 10:42"/>Wonke amakhosi la lamazwe awo athunjwa nguJoshuwa ekuhlaseleni kunye, ngenxa yokuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu ka-Israyeli, walwela u-Israyeli.<verse eid="JOS 10:42"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="JOS 10:43"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa waphindela laye wonke u-Israyeli ezihonqweni zaseGiligali.<verse eid="JOS 10:43"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 10"/>
  <chapter number="11" style="c" sid="JOS 11"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukunqotshwa Kwamakhosi Asenyakatho</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 11:1"/>Kwathi uJabhini inkosi yeHazori isizwa lokhu yathumela ilizwi kuJobhabhi inkosi yeMadoni lasemakhosini eShimroni le-Akhishafi, <verse eid="JOS 11:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 11:2"/>lasemakhosini enyakatho ayesezintabeni ze-Arabha eningizimu yeKhinerethi emawatheni amaqaqa entshonalanga kanye laseNafothi Dori entshonalanga; <verse eid="JOS 11:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 11:3"/>lakumaKhenani empumalanga lentshonalanga; lakuma-Amori, amaHithi, amaPherizi lamaJebusi elizweni elilamaqaqa; kanye lakumaHivi ngaphansi kweHemoni esabelweni seMizipha. <verse eid="JOS 11:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 11:4"/>Baphuma lamabutho abo wonke lenani elikhulu lamabhiza lezinqola, ibutho elikhulu, ubunengi lingangetshebetshebe okhunjini lolwandle. <verse eid="JOS 11:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 11:5"/>Wonke amakhosi la abambana asesakha izihonqo ndawonye eManzini aseMeromi, ukulwa labako-Israyeli.<verse eid="JOS 11:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 11:6"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuJoshuwa, “Ungabesabi, ngoba ngalesisikhathi kusasa ngizabanikela bonke kwabako-Israyeli sebefile. Uzaquma imisipha yamabhiza abo njalo utshise izihonqo zabo.”<verse eid="JOS 11:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 11:7"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa lebutho lakhe lonke bahlangana labo mathupha eManzini eMeromi wasebahlasela, <verse eid="JOS 11:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 11:8"/><char style="nd">uThixo</char> wabanikela esandleni sika-Israyeli. Babanqoba, baxotshana labo baze babafikisa eSidoni Enkulu kusiya eMisirefothi-Mayimi, leSigodini seMizipha empumalanga kwaze kwasala kungelamuntu ophilayo. <verse eid="JOS 11:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 11:9"/>UJoshuwa wenza kibo lokho ayekulaywe <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>: Waquma imisipha yamabhiza abo njalo watshisa izinqola zabo.<verse eid="JOS 11:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 11:10"/>Ngalesosikhathi uJoshuwa waphenduka wabuyela emuva wathumba iHazori wasehlasela inkosi yakuleyo ndawo ngenkemba. (IHazori yayiyisigodlo sayo yonke imibuso leyo.) <verse eid="JOS 11:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 11:11"/>Wonke umuntu owayephakathi kwayo wabhujiswa ngenkemba. Bababhubhisa baphela, abaze batshiya lutho oluphefumulayo, watshisa iHazori ngokwayo.<verse eid="JOS 11:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 11:12"/>UJoshuwa wathumba wonke amadolobho esikhosini lamakhosi awo wawahlasela ngenkemba. Wawabhubhisa wonke, njengokulaya kukaMosi inceku <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>. <verse eid="JOS 11:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 11:13"/>Kukanti-ke u-Israyeli kazange atshise loba yiwaphi amadolobho ayakhelwe emadundulwini ngaphandle kweHazori, eyatshiswa nguJoshuwa. <verse eid="JOS 11:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 11:14"/>Abako-Israyeli bathatha zaba ngezabo zonke impahla ababezithumbile okwakugoqela izifuyo zamadolobho la bahamba lakho kodwa bonke abantu bababhubhisa ngenkemba baphela du, bengatshiyi lutho oluphefumulayo. <verse eid="JOS 11:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 11:15"/>Njengoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> walaya inceku yakhe uMosi, uMosi laye walaya uJoshuwa, uJoshuwa wakwenza lokho: katshiyanga lutho lungenziwanga ezintweni zonke <char style="nd">uThixo</char> owazilaya uMosi.<verse eid="JOS 11:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOS 11:16"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa wathatha ilizwe lonke: ilizwe lamaqaqa, yonke iNegebi, isabelo sonke seGosheni, amawatha asentshonalanga, i-Arabha, lezintaba zako-Israyeli lamawatha azo, <verse eid="JOS 11:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOS 11:17"/>kusukela entabeni yeHalakhi, ephakama ngokuya eSeyiri, kusiya eBhali-Gadi esiGodini seLebhanoni ngaphansi kwentaba iHemoni. Wathumba wonke amakhosi awo, wawehlula, wawabulala. <verse eid="JOS 11:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOS 11:18"/>UJoshuwa walwa impi lawo wonke amakhosi okwesikhathi eside. <verse eid="JOS 11:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOS 11:19"/>Ngaphandle kwamaHivi ayehlala eGibhiyoni, kalikho idolobho loba elilodwa elenza isivumelwano sokuthula labako-Israyeli, kwabawathumba empini. <verse eid="JOS 11:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOS 11:20"/>Ngoba <char style="nd">kwakunguThixo</char> owenza inhliziyo zawo zaba lukhuni zafuna ukulwa impi lo-Israyeli, ukwenzela ukuthi enelise ukubachitha baphele, ebabhubhisa okungelazwelo, njengokulaywa kukaMosi <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>.<verse eid="JOS 11:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOS 11:21"/>Ngalesosikhathi uJoshuwa waphuma wawabhubhisa ama-Anakhi elizweni lamaqaqa: kusukela eHebhroni, eDebhiri le-Anabhi, kusukela elizweni lonke lamaqaqa akoJuda. UJoshuwa wabhubhisa wababhuqa bona kanye lamadolobho abo. <verse eid="JOS 11:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOS 11:22"/>Akula ma-Anakhi asala esabelweni sabako-Israyeli; ngaphandle kweGaza iGathi le-Ashidodi lapho okwasila abanye bakhona.<verse eid="JOS 11:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOS 11:23"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa wathumba ilizwe lonke njengoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> walaya uMosi, waselinika abako-Israyeli njengelifa kusiya ngokwahlukaniswa kwezizwana zabo. Ngakho-ke ilizwe laphumula ekulweni izimpi.<verse eid="JOS 11:23"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 11"/>
  <chapter number="12" style="c" sid="JOS 12"/>
  <para style="s1">Uluhlu Lwamakhosi Ehlulwayo</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 12:1"/>La ngamakhosi amazwe anqotshwa ngabako-Israyeli njalo alezabelo ezathunjwa empumalanga yeJodani, kusukela eDongeni lwase-Arinoni kusiya entabeni yaseHemoni, okugoqela lonke icele langempumalanga ye-Arabha:<verse eid="JOS 12:1"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 12:2"/>USihoni inkosi yama-Amori, wayebusa eHeshibhoni.</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="JOS 12:2">Wayebusa kusukela e-Aroweri emaphethelweni oDonga lwase-Arinoni, kusukela phakathi laphakathi kodonga kusiyafika emfuleni uJabhoki, oyiwo umngcele wama-Amoni. Lokhu kwakugoqela ingxenye yeGiliyadi.<verse eid="JOS 12:2"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 12:3"/>Wayebusa njalo empumalanga ye-Arabha kusukela olwandle lweKhinerethi kusiyafika olwandle lwe-Arabha (uLwandle lweTswayi) kusiya eBhethi-Jeshimothi, eningizimu phansanyana kwemithezuko yasePhisiga:<verse eid="JOS 12:3"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 12:4"/>Lelizwe lika-Ogi inkosi yaseBhashani, omunye wamaRefayi okucina owayebusa e-Ashitharothi le-Edreyi.<verse eid="JOS 12:4"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 12:5"/>Wabusa eNtabeni yaseHemoni, eSalekha, iBhashani yonke kusiya emngceleni wabantu beGeshuri leMahakhathi, lengxenye yeGiliyadi kusiya emngceleni kaSihoni inkosi yeHeshibhoni.<verse eid="JOS 12:5"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 12:6"/>UMosi inceku <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>, labako-Israyeli babanqoba. UMosi inceku <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> wanika ilizwe labo abakoRubheni labakoGadi lengxenye yesizwana sakoManase ukuthi libe ngelabo.<verse eid="JOS 12:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 12:7"/>La yiwo amakhosi elizwe lelo uJoshuwa labako-Israyeli abalithumbayo eceleni elisentshonalanga yeJodani, kusukela eBhali-Gadi esiGodini seLebhanoni kusiya eNtabeni yeHalakhi ekhangele eSeyiri (amazwe abo uJoshuwa wawanika njengelifa ezizwaneni zako-Israyeli kusiya ngezigaba zezizwana zabo, <verse eid="JOS 12:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 12:8"/>indawo elamaqaqa, amawatha asentshonalanga, i-Arabha, lemithezukweni yezintaba, inkangala leNegebi, amazwe amaHithi, ama-Amori, amaKhenani, amaPherizi, amaHivi, lamaJebusi):</para>
  <para style="b" vid="JOS 12:8"/>
  <para style="li4" vid="JOS 12:8">La ayengamakhosi:<verse eid="JOS 12:8"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 12:9"/>inkosi yeJerikho, eyodwa</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 12:9">inkosi ye-Ayi (eduze leBhetheli), eyodwa<verse eid="JOS 12:9"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 12:10"/>inkosi yeJerusalema, eyodwa</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 12:10">inkosi yeHebhroni, eyodwa<verse eid="JOS 12:10"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 12:11"/>inkosi yeJamuthi, eyodwa</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 12:11">inkosi yeLakhishi, eyodwa<verse eid="JOS 12:11"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 12:12"/>inkosi ye-Egiloni, eyodwa</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 12:12">inkosi yeGezeri, eyodwa<verse eid="JOS 12:12"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 12:13"/>inkosi yeDebhiri, eyodwa</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 12:13">inkosi yeBhethi-Gaderi, eyodwa<verse eid="JOS 12:13"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 12:14"/>inkosi yeHoma, eyodwa</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 12:14">inkosi ye-Aradi, eyodwa<verse eid="JOS 12:14"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 12:15"/>inkosi yeLibhina, eyodwa</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 12:15">inkosi ye-Adulami, eyodwa<verse eid="JOS 12:15"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOS 12:16"/>inkosi yeMakheda, eyodwa</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 12:16">inkosi yeBhetheli, eyodwa<verse eid="JOS 12:16"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOS 12:17"/>inkosi yeThaphuwa, eyodwa</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 12:17">inkosi yeHeferi, eyodwa<verse eid="JOS 12:17"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOS 12:18"/>inkosi ye-Afekhi, eyodwa</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 12:18">inkosi yeLasharoni, eyodwa<verse eid="JOS 12:18"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOS 12:19"/>inkosi yeMadoni, eyodwa</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 12:19">inkosi yeHazori, eyodwa<verse eid="JOS 12:19"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOS 12:20"/>inkosi yeShimron Meroni, eyodwa</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 12:20">inkosi ye-Akhishafi, eyodwa<verse eid="JOS 12:20"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOS 12:21"/>inkosi yeThanakhi, eyodwa</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 12:21">inkosi yeMegido, eyodwa<verse eid="JOS 12:21"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOS 12:22"/>inkosi yeKhedeshi, eyodwa</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 12:22">inkosi yeJokhiniyamu eseKhameli, eyodwa<verse eid="JOS 12:22"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOS 12:23"/>inkosi yeDori (eNafothi Dori), eyodwa</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 12:23">inkosi yeGoyimi eseGiligali, eyodwa<verse eid="JOS 12:23"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOS 12:24"/>inkosi yeThiza, eyodwa.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="JOS 12:24"/>
  <para style="li4" vid="JOS 12:24">Amakhosi angamatshumi amathathu lanye esewonke.<verse eid="JOS 12:24"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 12"/>
  <chapter number="13" style="c" sid="JOS 13"/>
  <para style="s1">Ilizwe Elisazathunjwa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 13:1"/>UJoshuwa esemdala njalo eseluphele kakhulu, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wathi kuye, “Usuluphele kakhulu, njalo lokhu usasalelwe yilizwe elikhulu kakhulu okumele ulithumbe.<verse eid="JOS 13:1"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 13:2"/>Nanti ilizwe elisaseleyo:</para>
  <para style="b" vid="JOS 13:2"/>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 13:2">zonke izabelo zamaFilistiya lamaGeshuri: <verse eid="JOS 13:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 13:3"/>kusukela emfuleni uShihori empumalanga yeGibhithe kusiya esabelweni se-Ekroni enyakatho, lonke libaliswa njengelamaKhenani lanxa libanjwe ngababusi beFilistiya abahlanu eGaza, e-Ashidodi, e-Ashikheloni, eGathi le-Ekroni</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 13:3">ilizwe lama-Avi; <verse eid="JOS 13:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 13:4"/>kusukela eningizimu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 13:4">lonke ilizwe lamaKhenani, kusukela eMeyara yamaSidoni kusiyafika e-Afekhi, isabelo sama-Amori,<verse eid="JOS 13:4"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 13:5"/>indawo yamaGebhali;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 13:5">layo yonke iLebhanoni ngempumalanga, kusukela eBhali-Gadi ngaphansi kweNtaba yeHemoni kusiya eLebho Hamathi.<verse eid="JOS 13:5"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 13:6"/>Bonke abakhele ezabelweni ezisezintabeni kusukela eLebhanoni kusiya eMisirefothi-Mayimi, okutsho wonke amaSidoni, mina ngokwami ngizabaxotsha phambi kwabako-Israyeli. Wobani leqiniso lokuthi lelilizwe labelwe abako-Israyeli ukuze libe yilifa labo njengokulilaya kwami, <verse eid="JOS 13:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 13:7"/>njalo lilabe njengelifa phakathi kwezizwana eziyisificamunwemunye lengxenye yesizwana sakoManase.”<verse eid="JOS 13:7"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukwabiwa Kwelizwe Elisempumalanga YeJodani</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 13:8"/>Eyinye ingxenye yakoManase, eyakoRubheni leyakoGadi yayizuze ilifa eyalinikwa nguMosi empumalanga yeJodani njengalokho inceku <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> eyayibaphe lona.<verse eid="JOS 13:8"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 13:9"/>Lasuka e-Aroweri emaphethelweni oDonga lwe-Arinoni lasedolobheni eliphakathi kodonga, njalo ligoqela amagceke eMedebha kusiyafika eDibhoni, <verse eid="JOS 13:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 13:10"/>lamadolobho wonke kaSihoni inkosi yama-Amori, owabusa eHeshibhoni, kusiyafika emngceleni wama-Amoni.<verse eid="JOS 13:10"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 13:11"/>Laligoqela iGiliyadi, isabelo sabantu baseGeshuri leMahakhathi, leNtaba yonke yeHemoni leBhashani yonke kusiyafika eSalekha, <verse eid="JOS 13:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 13:12"/>okutsho ukuthi, umbuso wonke ka-Ogi eBhashani, yena owabusa e-Ashitharothi le-Edreyi njalo wayengomunye wamaRefayi ayelokhu esaphila. UMosi wayebanqobile wathatha ilizwe labo. <verse eid="JOS 13:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 13:13"/>Kodwa abako-Israyeli kabazange babaxotshe abantu beGeshuri leMahakhathi, yikho lokhu behlala phakathi kwabako-Israyeli kuze kube lamhlanje.<verse eid="JOS 13:13"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 13:14"/>Kodwa abesizwana sabaLevi kazange abanike ilifa, njengoba iminikelo eyayisenziwa ngomlilo <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu wako-Israyeli iyilifa labo njengokubathembisa kwakhe.<verse eid="JOS 13:14"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 13:15"/>Lokhu yikho uMosi akunika isizwana sakoRubheni, usendo lunye ngalunye:<verse eid="JOS 13:15"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOS 13:16"/>Isigaba esisuka e-Aroweri emaphethelweni oDonga lwe-Arinoni, lokusuka edolobheni eliphakathi koDonga lawo wonke amagceke adabula eMedebha <verse eid="JOS 13:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOS 13:17"/>kusiya eHeshibhoni lawo wonke amadolobho asemagcekeni agoqela iDibhoni, iBhamothi-Bhali, iBhethi-Bhali-Meyoni, <verse eid="JOS 13:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOS 13:18"/>iJahazi, iKhedemothi, iMefahathi, <verse eid="JOS 13:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOS 13:19"/>iKhiriyathayimi, iSibhima, iZerethi-Shahari eqaqeni olusesigodini, <verse eid="JOS 13:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOS 13:20"/>iBhethi-Pheyori, lemithezuko yasePhisiga, leBhethi-Jeshimothi, <verse eid="JOS 13:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOS 13:21"/>wonke amadolobho asemagcekeni lombuso wonke kaSihoni inkosi yama-Amori, owayebusa eHeshibhoni. UMosi wayemehlule yena lezinduna zamaMidiyani, u-Evi, uRekhemu, uZuri, uHuri, loRebha, wonke engamakhosana amanyane loSihoni owayehlala kulelolizwe. <verse eid="JOS 13:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOS 13:22"/>Phezu kwalabo ababulawa empini abako-Israyeli babebulele ngenkemba uBhalamu indodana kaBheyori, owayeyisanuse.<verse eid="JOS 13:22"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOS 13:23"/>Umngcele wamaRubheni wawusokhunjini lweJodani. Amadolobho la lemizana yawo ayeyilifa labakoRubheni, usendo lunye ngalunye:<verse eid="JOS 13:23"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOS 13:24"/>Lokhu yikho uMosi akupha isizwana sakoGadi usendo lunye ngalunye:<verse eid="JOS 13:24"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOS 13:25"/>Isabelo seJazeri, amadolobho wonke eGiliyadi lengxenye yelizwe lama-Amoni kusiyafika e-Aroweri, eduzane leRabha; <verse eid="JOS 13:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOS 13:26"/>lokusuka eHeshibhoni kusiya eRamathi Mizipha leBhethonimi, lokusuka eMahanayimi kusiya esigabeni seDebhiri; <verse eid="JOS 13:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOS 13:27"/>esigodini iBhethi-Haramu, iBhethi-Nimra, iSukhothi leZafoni lawo wonke umbuso kaSihoni inkosi yeHeshibhoni (icele elisempumalanga yeJodani, isabelo esisekucineni kolwandle lweKhinerethi).<verse eid="JOS 13:27"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOS 13:28"/>Amadolobho la ndawonye lemizana yawo ayeyilifa labakoGadi; usendo lunye ngalunye.<verse eid="JOS 13:28"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOS 13:29"/>Lokhu yikho uMosi ayekunike ingxenye yesizwana sakoManase, okutsho ingxenye yemuli eyayiyinzalo kaManase, usendo lunye ngalunye:<verse eid="JOS 13:29"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="JOS 13:30"/>Umango owawusuka eMahanayimi ugoqela iBhashani, wonke umbuso ka-Ogi inkosi yaseBhashani, yonke imizana yeJayiri eBhashani, amadolobho angamatshumi ayisithupha, <verse eid="JOS 13:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="JOS 13:31"/>ingxenye yeGiliyadi, le-Ashitharothi le-Edreyi (amadolobho obukhosi ka-Ogi eBhashani).</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="JOS 13:31">Lokhu kwakungokwezizukulwane zikaMakhiri indodana kaManase, kungokwengxenye yamadodana kaMakhiri usendo lunye ngalunye.<verse eid="JOS 13:31"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="JOS 13:32"/>Leli yilo ilifa uMosi ayelabile lapho esasemagcekeni eMowabi ngaphetsheya kweJodani empumalanga yeJerikho. <verse eid="JOS 13:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="JOS 13:33"/>Kodwa esizwaneni sabaLevi, uMosi kazange asabele ilifa; <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu wako-Israyeli, nguye ilifa labo njengokubathembisa kwakhe.<verse eid="JOS 13:33"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 13"/>
  <chapter number="14" style="c" sid="JOS 14"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukwabiwa Komhlaba ENtshonalanga YeJodani</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 14:1"/>Lezi yizo izindawo abako-Israyeli abazamukela njengelifa elizweni laseKhenani, u-Eliyazari umphristi, uJoshuwa indodana kaNuni lezinhloko zezizwana zako-Israyeli abazabela zona. <verse eid="JOS 14:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 14:2"/>Ilifa labo labiwa ngokwenza inkatho ezizwaneni eziyisificamunwemunye lengxenye, njengokulaya <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> ngoMosi. <verse eid="JOS 14:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 14:3"/>UMosi wayenike izizwe ezimbili lengxenye ilifa lazo empumalanga yeJodani, kodwa wayengabelanga abaLevi ilifa phakathi kwazo, <verse eid="JOS 14:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 14:4"/>ngoba amadodana kaJosefa ayeyizizwana ezimbili, esikaManase lesika-Efrayimi. AbaLevi kabazuzanga sabelo ngaphandle kwamadolobho okuhlala lamadlelo emihlambi yezimvu leyenkomo. <verse eid="JOS 14:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 14:5"/>Ngakho abako-Israyeli behlukanisa umhlaba, njengokulaywa kukaMosi <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>.<verse eid="JOS 14:5"/></para>
  <para style="s1">IHebhroni Inikwa UKhalebi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 14:6"/>Amadoda akoJuda aya kuJoshuwa eGiligali, uKhalebi indodana kaJefune umKhenizi wathi kuye, “Uyakwazi ukuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wathini kuMosi umuntu kaNkulunkulu eKhadeshi Bhaneya ngawe lami. <verse eid="JOS 14:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 14:7"/>Ngangileminyaka engamatshumi amane lapho uMosi inceku <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> yangithuma ngisuka eKhadeshi Bhaneya ukuyahlola ilizwe. Ngaletha kuye umbiko owawuphathelane lemibono yami, <verse eid="JOS 14:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 14:8"/>kodwa abazalwane engahamba labo benza ukuthi inhliziyo zabantu zithuthumele ngokwesaba. Mina, lanxa kunjalo, ngalandela <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wami ngenhliziyo yami yonke. <verse eid="JOS 14:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 14:9"/><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">14.9 UDutheronomi 1.36</char></note>Ngakho ngalelolanga uMosi wafunga kimi wathi, ‘Umhlabathi lowo onyathelwe yizinyawo zakho uzakuba yilifa lakho labantwabakho kuze kube nini lanini, ngenxa yokuthi ulandele <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wami ngenhliziyo yakho yonke.’<verse eid="JOS 14:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 14:10"/>Ngakho-ke, njengoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wayethembisile, usengigcine ngiphila okweminyaka engamatshumi amane lanhlanu kusukela ngezikhathi lapho akhuluma lokhu kuMosi, u-Israyeli esazulazula enkangala. Ngakho nanku sengilapha lamuhla, sengileminyaka yokuzalwa engamatshumi ayisificaminwembili lanhlanu! <verse eid="JOS 14:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 14:11"/>Lokhu ngisaqinile lanamuhla njengelanga uMosi angithuma ngalo; lokhu ngiselamandla okuyakulwa impi khathesi okufanana lalokho engangiyikho khona ngalesosikhathi. <verse eid="JOS 14:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 14:12"/>Ngakho nginika lelilizwe lamaqaqa engalithenjiswa <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> ngalelolanga. Wena ngokwakho wezwa ngalesosikhathi ukuthi ama-Anakhi ayekhona lapho njalo amadolobho awo ayemakhulu ehonqolozelwe, kodwa ngokuncediswa <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>, ngizawaxotsha njengokutsho kwakhe.”<verse eid="JOS 14:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 14:13"/>Ngakho UJoshuwa wabusisa uKhalebi indodana kaJefune, wamnika iHebhroni yaba yilifa lakhe. <verse eid="JOS 14:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 14:14"/>Ngakho iHebhroni yaba lilifa likaKhalebi indodana kaJefune umKhenizi kusukela ngalesosikhathi ngenxa yokuthi walandela <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu ka-Israyeli ngenhliziyo yakhe yonke. <verse eid="JOS 14:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 14:15"/>(IHebhroni yayithiwa yiKhiriyathi Aribha ibizwa ngo-Abhe owayeyindoda eyayiyisikhulu esesabekayo phakathi kwama-Anakhi).</para>
  <para style="p" vid="JOS 14:15">Ngakho ilizwe laba lokuphumula ekulweni izimpi.<verse eid="JOS 14:15"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 14"/>
  <chapter number="15" style="c" sid="JOS 15"/>
  <para style="s1">Isabelo SikaJuda</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 15:1"/>Isabelo sesizwe sikaJuda, usendo lunye ngalunye sasiqhele sehla sayafika elizweni le-Edomi, sisiyakhawula eNkangala yeZini eningizimu kude le.<verse eid="JOS 15:1"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 15:2"/>Umngcele wabo weningizimu wawuqalisela ethekwini oluseningizimu emaphethelweni oLwandle lweTswayi, <verse eid="JOS 15:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 15:3"/>uchaphela eningizimu yoMkhandlu weNkume, uqhubeka usiya eZini, usiyaphutsha eningizimu yeKhadeshi Bhaneya. Wasusedlula eHezironi usiyafika e-Adari wabhoda unquma wayaphutsha ususeKhakha. <verse eid="JOS 15:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 15:4"/>Wasusedlula usiya e-Azimoni usiyaxhumana lesiHotsha saseGibhithe, uphelela olwandle. Lo yiwo umngcele wabo waseningizimu.<verse eid="JOS 15:4"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 15:5"/>Umngcele wempumalanga luLwandle lweTswayi kuze kufike lapho okuthela khona iJodani.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 15:5">Umngcele weningizimu waqalela okhunjini lolwandle ekuqaleni kweJodani, <verse eid="JOS 15:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 15:6"/>wakhwela usiya eBhethi-Hogla, wabuye waqhubeka usiya Bhethi-Arabha uqonda eLitsheni likaBhohani indodana kaRubheni. <verse eid="JOS 15:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 15:7"/>Umngcele wasuqansa usiya eDebhiri usuka esigodini sika-Akhori, wasujika usiya enyakatho ukhangela eGiligali ekhangelane loMkhandlu ka-Adumimu eningizimu yodonga. Waqhubeka usiya emanzini ase-Eni Shemeshi wasufika e-Eni Rogeli. <verse eid="JOS 15:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 15:8"/>Wasuqonda esigodini seBheni-Hinomu emthezukweni wangeningizimu yedolobho lamaJebusi (okutsho iJerusalema). Usuka lapho waqansa phezu koqaqa entshonalanga yesigodi seHinomu ekucineni kwangenyakatho yesigodi seRefayi. <verse eid="JOS 15:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 15:9"/>Usuka engqongeni yoqaqa, umngcele waqonda emthonjeni wamanzi aseNefuthowa, wasuphutsha emadolobheni eNtabeni ye-Efroni wasusehla usiya eBhala (okutsho iKhiriyathi-Jeyarimi). <verse eid="JOS 15:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 15:10"/>Wasujika usiya entshonalanga usuka eBhala usiya entabeni yeSeyiri, wedlula emthezukweni wangenyakatho yentaba iJeyarimi (okutsho iKhesaloni) waqhubeka usiya eBhethi-Shemeshi uchaphela eThimina. <verse eid="JOS 15:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 15:11"/>Waqonda emthezukweni wenyakatho owe-Ekroni, wajika ukhangele eShikheroni, wedlule usiya eNtabeni yeBhala wafika eJabhiniyeli. Umngcele waphelela olwandle.<verse eid="JOS 15:11"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 15:12"/>Umngcele wangentshonalanga likhumbi loLwandle oLukhulu.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="JOS 15:12"/>
  <para style="li4" vid="JOS 15:12">Le yiyo imingcele eyayigombolozele abantu bakoJuda usendo lunye ngalunye.<verse eid="JOS 15:12"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 15:13"/>Njengokulaya <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> kuye, uJoshuwa wanika uKhalebi indodana kaJefune ingxenye eseJuda, iKhiriyathi Aribha, okutsho iHebhroni (u-Abha wayengukhokho ka-Anakhi). <verse eid="JOS 15:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 15:14"/>Esuka eHebhroni uKhalebi waxotsha ama-Anakhi amathathu abalisa uSheshayi, u-Ahimani loThalimayi abantwana baka-Anakhi. <verse eid="JOS 15:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 15:15"/>Esuka lapho wahamba ehlasela abantu ababehlala eDebhiri (okwakuthiwa yiKhiriyathi-Sefa). <verse eid="JOS 15:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOS 15:16"/>UKhalebi wathi, “Ngizakwendisela indodakazi yami u-Akhisa endodeni ezahlasela ithumbe iKhiriyathi-Sefa.” <verse eid="JOS 15:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOS 15:17"/>U-Othiniyeli indodana kaKhenazi, umfowabo kaKhalebi, wayithumba; ngakho uKhalebi wendisela indodakazi yakhe u-Akhisa kuye.<verse eid="JOS 15:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOS 15:18"/>Ngelinye ilanga u-Akhisa wafika ku-Othiniyeli wamkhuthaza ukuthi acele insimu kuyise. Lapho esehlile kubabhemi wakhe, uKhalebi wambuza wathi, “Kuyini engingakwenzela khona?”<verse eid="JOS 15:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOS 15:19"/>Waphendula wathi, “Ngicela ungenzele umusa obalulekileyo. Njengoba unginike umhlaba eNegebi, ngicela unginike lemithombo yamanzi.” Ngakho uKhalebi wamnika imithombo eyayingaphezulu leyayingaphansi.<verse eid="JOS 15:19"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOS 15:20"/>Leli lilifa lesizwe sikaJuda ngezinsendo zaso:<verse eid="JOS 15:20"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOS 15:21"/>Amadolobho aseningizimu kwesizwe sikaJuda eNegebi ekuyeni emngceleni we-Edomi ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="JOS 15:21">IKhabhizeli, i-Ederi, iJaguri, <verse eid="JOS 15:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOS 15:22"/>iKhina, iDimona, i-Adada, <verse eid="JOS 15:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOS 15:23"/>iKhedeshi, iHazori, i-Ithinani, <verse eid="JOS 15:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOS 15:24"/>iZifi, iThelemu, iBheyalothi, <verse eid="JOS 15:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOS 15:25"/>iHazori-Hadatha, iKheriyothi Hezironi (okutsho iHazori), <verse eid="JOS 15:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOS 15:26"/>i-Amamu, iShema, iMolada, <verse eid="JOS 15:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOS 15:27"/>iHazari-Gada, iHeshimoni, iBhethi Phelethi, <verse eid="JOS 15:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOS 15:28"/>iHazari-Shuwali, iBherishebha, iBhiziyothiya, <verse eid="JOS 15:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOS 15:29"/>iBhala, i-Iyimu, i-Ezema, <verse eid="JOS 15:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="JOS 15:30"/>i-Elitholadi, iKhesili, iHoma <verse eid="JOS 15:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="JOS 15:31"/>iZikhilagi, iMadimana, iSansana, <verse eid="JOS 15:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="JOS 15:32"/>iLebhayothi, iShilihimu, i-Ayini leRimoni, esewonke kwakungamadolobho angamatshumi amabili lesificamunwemunye lemizana yawo.<verse eid="JOS 15:32"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="JOS 15:33"/>Emawatheni asentshonalanga kwakulamadolobho la:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="JOS 15:33">I-Eshithawoli, iZora, i-Ashina, <verse eid="JOS 15:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="JOS 15:34"/>iZanowa, i-Eni-Ganimu, iThaphuwa, i-Enamu, <verse eid="JOS 15:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="JOS 15:35"/>iJamuthi, i-Adulami, iSokho, i-Azekha, <verse eid="JOS 15:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="JOS 15:36"/>iShaharayimu, i-Adithayimu leGedera (kumbe iGederothayimu) amadolobho alitshumi lane lemizi yawo.<verse eid="JOS 15:36"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="JOS 15:37"/>IZenani, iHadasha, iMigidali-Gadi, <verse eid="JOS 15:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="JOS 15:38"/>iDiliyeni, iMizipha, iJokhitheyeli, <verse eid="JOS 15:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="JOS 15:39"/>iLakhishi, iBhozikhathi, i-Egiloni, <verse eid="JOS 15:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="JOS 15:40"/>iKhabhoni, iLahimasi, iKhithilishi <verse eid="JOS 15:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="JOS 15:41"/>iGederothi, iBhethi-Dagoni, iNahama leMakheda, amadolobho alitshumi lesithupha lemizi yawo.<verse eid="JOS 15:41"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="JOS 15:42"/>ILibhina, i-Etheri, i-Ashani, <verse eid="JOS 15:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="JOS 15:43"/>i-Ifitha, i-Ashina, iNezibhi, <verse eid="JOS 15:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="JOS 15:44"/>iKheyila, i-Akhizibhi leMaresha, amadolobho ayisificamunwemunye lemizi yawo.<verse eid="JOS 15:44"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="JOS 15:45"/>I-Ekroni, lemizana eyigqagqeleyo; <verse eid="JOS 15:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="JOS 15:46"/>entshonalanga ye-Ekroni, wonke ayeseduzane le-Ashidodi, ndawonye lemizana yawo; <verse eid="JOS 15:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="JOS 15:47"/>i-Ashidodi lemizana eyigqagqeleyo leGaza, imizana eyigqagqeleyo kusiyafika esiHotsheni saseGibhithe lekhunjini loLwandle oLukhulu.<verse eid="JOS 15:47"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="48" style="v" sid="JOS 15:48"/>Elizweni lamaqaqa kwakule:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="JOS 15:48">IShamiri, iJathiri, iSokho, <verse eid="JOS 15:48"/><verse number="49" style="v" sid="JOS 15:49"/>iDana, iKhiriyathi-Sana (okutsho iDebhiri), <verse eid="JOS 15:49"/><verse number="50" style="v" sid="JOS 15:50"/>i-Anabhi, i-Eshithemo, i-Animi, <verse eid="JOS 15:50"/><verse number="51" style="v" sid="JOS 15:51"/>iGosheni, iHoloni leGilo, amadolobho alitshumi lanye lemizana yawo.<verse eid="JOS 15:51"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="52" style="v" sid="JOS 15:52"/>I-Arabhu, iDuma, i-Eshani, <verse eid="JOS 15:52"/><verse number="53" style="v" sid="JOS 15:53"/>iJanimu, iBhethi-Thaphuwa, i-Afeka, <verse eid="JOS 15:53"/><verse number="54" style="v" sid="JOS 15:54"/>iHumtha, iKhiriyathi Aribha (okutsho iHebhroni) leZiwori, amadolobho ayisificamunwemunye lemizana yawo.<verse eid="JOS 15:54"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="55" style="v" sid="JOS 15:55"/>IMawoni, iKhameli, iZifi, iJutha, <verse eid="JOS 15:55"/><verse number="56" style="v" sid="JOS 15:56"/>iJezerili, iJokideyamu, iZanowa, <verse eid="JOS 15:56"/><verse number="57" style="v" sid="JOS 15:57"/>iKhayini, iGibhiya leThimina, amadolobho alitshumi lemizana yawo.<verse eid="JOS 15:57"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="58" style="v" sid="JOS 15:58"/>IHalihuli, iBhethi Zuri, iGedori, <verse eid="JOS 15:58"/><verse number="59" style="v" sid="JOS 15:59"/>iMaharathi, iBhethi-Anothi le-Elithekhoni, amadolobho ayisithupha lemizana yawo.<verse eid="JOS 15:59"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="60" style="v" sid="JOS 15:60"/>IKhiriyathi-Bhali (okutsho ukuthi iKhiriyathi-Jeyarimi) leRabha, amadolobho amabili lemizana yawo.<verse eid="JOS 15:60"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="61" style="v" sid="JOS 15:61"/>Enkangala:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="JOS 15:61">IBhethi-Arabha, iMidini, iSekhakha, <verse eid="JOS 15:61"/><verse number="62" style="v" sid="JOS 15:62"/>iNibhishani, iDolobho letswayi le-Eni-Gedi, amadolobho ayisithupha lemizana yawo.<verse eid="JOS 15:62"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="63" style="v" sid="JOS 15:63"/>UJuda wehluleka ukususa amaJebusi ayehlala eJerusalema; lanamuhla amaJebusi lokhu ehlala lapho labantu bakoJuda.<verse eid="JOS 15:63"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 15"/>
  <chapter number="16" style="c" sid="JOS 16"/>
  <para style="s1">Isabelo Sika-Efrayimi LoManase</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 16:1"/>Isabelo sikaJosefa saqala eJodani, empumalanga yamanzi eJerikho, sakhwela sisuka lapho sisiya enkangala singena elizweni lamaqaqa eBhetheli. <verse eid="JOS 16:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 16:2"/>Sadabula sisuka eBhetheli (okutsho iLuzi) sachaphela esabelweni sama-Arikhithi e-Atharothi, <verse eid="JOS 16:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 16:3"/>sehlela entshonalanga esabelweni samaJafilethi sisiyabamba ekhunjini lweBhethi-Horoni, sibuye siqonde eGezeri, sisiyaphelela olwandle.<verse eid="JOS 16:3"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 16:4"/>Ngakho uManase lo-Efrayimi, izizukulwane zikaJosefa, bemukela ilifa labo.<verse eid="JOS 16:4"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 16:5"/>Leli kwakulilizwe lika-Efrayimi ngokosendo lwakhe:</para>
  <para style="b" vid="JOS 16:5"/>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 16:5">Umngcele welifa labo wawusuka e-Atharothi-Ada empumalanga usiya eBhethi-Horoni Ephezulu <verse eid="JOS 16:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 16:6"/>waqhubeka usiya olwandle. Usuka eMikhimethathi enyakatho wajika empumalanga usiya eThahanathi-Shilo, usedlula eJanowa empumalanga. <verse eid="JOS 16:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 16:7"/>Wasusehlela phansi usuka eJanowa usiya e-Atharothi leNara, wagudla iJerikho wayaphutshela kuJodani. <verse eid="JOS 16:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 16:8"/>Usuka eThaphuwa umngcele waya entshonalanga eDongeni lweKhana wayaphelela olwandle. Leli kwakuyilifa lesizwana sako-Efrayimi, usendo lunye ngalunye.<verse eid="JOS 16:8"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 16:9"/>Wawugoqela njalo wonke amadolobho lemizana yawo eyayehlukaniselwe abako-Efrayimi phakathi kwelifa labakoManase.<verse eid="JOS 16:9"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 16:10"/>Kabazange bawadudule amaKhenani ayehlala eGezeri; kuze kube lamhla amaKhenani ahlala phakathi kwabantu bako-Efrayimi kodwa besenziswa umsebenzi wesibhalo.<verse eid="JOS 16:10"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 16"/>
  <chapter number="17" style="c" sid="JOS 17"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 17:1"/>Lesi kwakuyisabelo sesizwana sikaManase njengezibulo likaJosefa. UMakhiri izibulo likaManase, ukhokho wamaGiliyadi, wathatha iGiliyadi leBhashani ngenxa yokuthi amaMakhire ayengamaqhawe amakhulu. <verse eid="JOS 17:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 17:2"/>Ngakho isabelo lesi sasingesabantu bonke bakoManase, insendo zika-Abhiyezeri, uHelekhi, u-Asiriyeli, uShekhemu, uHeferi loShemida. Lezi ngezinye izizukulwane zesilisa zikaManase indodana kaJosefa ngokwensendo zazo.<verse eid="JOS 17:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 17:3"/>UZelofehadi indodana kaHeferi, indodana kaGiliyadi, indodana kaMakhiri indodana kaManase, wayengelamadodana kodwa wayelamadodakazi wodwa, amabizo awo kwakunguMahila, uNowa, uHogila, uMilikha loThiza. <verse eid="JOS 17:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 17:4"/>Aya ku-Eliyazari umphristi, loJoshuwa indodana kaNuni kanye labakhokheli athi, “<char style="nd">UThixo</char> walaya uMosi ukuthi asabele ilifa kanye labanewethu.” Ngakho uJoshuwa wabanika ilifa ndawonye labanewabo bakayise, kulandelwa umlayo <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>. <verse eid="JOS 17:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 17:5"/>Isabelo sikaManase sasigoqela iziqinti ezilitshumi zomhlabathi emhlubulweni weGiliyadi leBhashani empumalanga yeJodani, <verse eid="JOS 17:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 17:6"/>ngenxa yokuthi amadodakazi esizwana sikaManase athola ilifa kanye labafowabo. IGiliyadi yayingeyezizukulwana zikaManase.<verse eid="JOS 17:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 17:7"/>Ilizwe likaManase lalisukela e-Asheri lisiya eMikhimethathi empumalanga kweShekhemu. Umngcele wawudabula usiya usiyagoqela abantu ababehlala e-Eni-Thaphuwa. <verse eid="JOS 17:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 17:8"/>(UManase wayelomhlaba elizweni leThaphuwa, kodwa iThaphuwa ngokwayo, emngceleni kaManase, yayingeyama-Efrayimi.) <verse eid="JOS 17:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 17:9"/>Umngcele waqhubeka eningizimu usiya oDongeni lweKhana. Kwakulamadolobho ka-Efrayimi ayakhelwe phakathi kwamadolobho kaManase, kodwa umngcele kaManase wawulicele langenyakatho lodonga njalo uphelela olwandle. <verse eid="JOS 17:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 17:10"/>Eningizimu ilizwe lalingelika-Efrayimi, enyakatho lingelikaManase. Ilizwe likaManase lalifika olwandle njalo lingcelezelane lo-Asheri enyakatho kanye lo-Isakhari empumalanga.<verse eid="JOS 17:10"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 17:11"/>Phakathi kuka-Isakhari lo-Asheri uManase wayeloBhethi-Shani, u-Ibhiliyami labantu beDori, abe-Endo, abeThanakhi leMegido, ndawonye lemizana ababakhelane layo (owesithathu eluhlwini kwakunguNafothi).<verse eid="JOS 17:11"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 17:12"/>Kodwa-ke abakoManase kabenelisanga ukuthatha amadolobho la ngoba amaKhenani ayezimisele ukuhlala kuleyondawo. <verse eid="JOS 17:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 17:13"/>Lanxa kunjalo, kwathi abako-Israyeli sebelamandla amakhulu, benza amaKhenani izigqili zabo kodwa kababaxotshanga kokuphela.<verse eid="JOS 17:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 17:14"/>Abantu bakoJosefa bathi kuJoshuwa, “Kungani lisinike isabelo esisodwa kuphela lengxenye eyodwa yelifa na? Singabantu abanengi kakhulu njalo <char style="nd">uThixo</char> usibusise kakhulu.”<verse eid="JOS 17:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 17:15"/>UJoshuwa wabaphendula wathi; “Nxa libanengi kakhulu, njalo nxa ilizwe lamaqaqa elako-Efrayimi lilincinyane kini, ngenani eguswini liyecenta umhlaba ube ngowenu elizweni lamaPherizi lelamaRefayi.”<verse eid="JOS 17:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOS 17:16"/>Abantu bakoJosefa baphendula bathi, “Ilizwe lamaqaqa kaliseneli njalo amaKhenani wonke ahlala emagcekeni alezinqola zensimbi, bonke abaseBhethi-Shani lemizana yakhona lalabo ababehlala esigodini seJezerili.”<verse eid="JOS 17:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOS 17:17"/>Kodwa uJoshuwa wakhuluma labendlu kaJosefa, ku-Efrayimi loManase wathi, “Libanengi njalo lilamandla amakhulu kakhulu. Kalisoze libe lesabelo esisodwa kuphela, <verse eid="JOS 17:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOS 17:18"/>kodwa lelizwe lamaqaqa aliligusu. Licenteni lize liyefika lapho eliphelela khona kube ngelenu; lanxa amaKhenani elezinqola zensimbi njalo lanxa elamandla, lingawaxotsha.”<verse eid="JOS 17:18"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 17"/>
  <chapter number="18" style="c" sid="JOS 18"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukwabiwa Kwelizwe Elalisele</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 18:1"/>Ibandla lonke lako-Israyeli labuthana eShilo laselimisa ithente lokuhlangana khonapho. Ilizwe lalethwa ngaphansi kombuso wabo, <verse eid="JOS 18:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 18:2"/>kodwa kwakulokhu kulezizwana zako-Israyeli eziyisikhombisa ezazingakemukeli ilifa lazo.<verse eid="JOS 18:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 18:3"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa wathi kwabako-Israyeli, “Lizakuma okwesikhathi esingakanani lingakathathi ilizwe <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu wabokhokho benu alinike lona na? <verse eid="JOS 18:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 18:4"/>Khethani amadoda amathathu esizweni sinye ngasinye. Ngizawathuma ukuthi ayehlola ilizwe abeseloba ngesimo salo, kusiya ngelifa lesizwana ngasinye. Azaphenduka kimi. <verse eid="JOS 18:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 18:5"/>Lizakwaba umhlaba ube yizigaba eziyisikhombisa. UJuda uzaqhubeka eselizweni lakhe eningizimu njalo indlu kaJosefa iselizweni layo enyakatho. <verse eid="JOS 18:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 18:6"/>Ngemva kokuba selibhale izimo zezigaba eziyisikhombisa zelizwe, lizilethe kimi lapha njalo ngizalenzela inkatho phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wethu. <verse eid="JOS 18:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 18:7"/>Kodwa abaLevi kabayikuzuza lutho phakathi kwenu, ngoba umsebenzi wobuphristi <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> yilifa labo. Njalo uGadi, uRubheni lengxenye yesizwe sikaManase sebathola ilifa labo eceleni elingasempumalanga yeJodani. UMosi inceku <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> wabanika lona.”<verse eid="JOS 18:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 18:8"/>Kwathi amadoda engena indlela esiyahlola umhlaba, uJoshuwa wawalaya wathi, “Hambani liyehlola umhlaba beselibhala isimo sawo. Emva kwalokho beseliphenduka kimi, khona ngizalenzela inkatho lapha eShilo phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>.” <verse eid="JOS 18:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 18:9"/>Ngakho amadoda asuka adabula phakathi kwelizwe. Abhala isimo salo emqulwini, idolobho ngedolobho, ezigabeni eziyisikhombisa, asephindela kuJoshuwa esihonqweni seShilo.<verse eid="JOS 18:9"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 18:10"/>UJoshuwa wawenzela inkatho eShilo phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>, njalo lapho wabela ilizwe kwabako-Israyeli kusiya ngokwehlukaniswa kwezizwana zabo.<verse eid="JOS 18:10"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isabelo SikaBhenjamini</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 18:11"/>Inkatho yakuqala yawela esizwaneni sakoBhenjamini ngensendo zaso. Ilizwe labo elabiwayo laliphakathi kwezizwana zakoJuda loJosefa:<verse eid="JOS 18:11"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 18:12"/>Eceleni elisenyakatho umngcele wabo wawuqalisela kuJodani, usedlula emthezukweni wangenyakatho yeJerikho usiya entshonalanga elizweni elilamaqaqa, uthutshela enkangala yeBhethi-Aveni. <verse eid="JOS 18:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 18:13"/>Usuka lapho wawuchaphela emthezukweni weningizimu weLuzi (okutsho iBhetheli) usehlela e-Atharothi-Ada eqaqeni eliseningizimu ngaphansi kweBhethi-Horoni.<verse eid="JOS 18:13"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 18:14"/>Usuka eqaqeni elikhangelane leBhethi-Horoni eningizimu ulandela icele elisentshonalanga wasuthutshela eKhiriyathi-Bhali (okutsho iKhiriyathi-Jeyarimi) idolobho labantu bakoJuda. Leli kwakulicele elisentshonalanga.<verse eid="JOS 18:14"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 18:15"/>Icele leningizimu laliqalisela emaphethelweni asentshonalanga kweKhiriyathi-Jeyarimi, njalo umngcele waba semthonjeni wamanzi eNefuthowa. <verse eid="JOS 18:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOS 18:16"/>Umngcele wehla waya ewatheni lentaba ekhangelane leSigodi seBheni-Hinomu, enyakatho yeSigodi seRefayi. Waqhubeka usehla eSigodini seHinomu ulandela umthezuko wedolobho lamaJebusi usiya e-Eni Rogeli. <verse eid="JOS 18:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOS 18:17"/>Wasubhoda usiya enyakatho, waya e-Eni Shemeshi, waqhubeka usiya eGelilothi ekhangele uMkhandlu we-Adumimu, wehla phansi usiya elitsheni likaBhohani indodana kaRubheni. <verse eid="JOS 18:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOS 18:18"/>Waqhubeka ukhangele enyakatho, emthezukweni weBhethi Arabha usehla ungena e-Arabha. <verse eid="JOS 18:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOS 18:19"/>Wasusiya emthezukweni ongasenyakatho eBhethi-Hogla wasuphumela ewatheni elingenyakatho koLwandle lweTswayi lapho okuthela khona iJodani eningizimu. Lo kwakungumngcele oseningizimu.<verse eid="JOS 18:19"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOS 18:20"/>IJodani yenza umngcele eceleni langempumalanga.</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="JOS 18:20">Le kwakuyimingcele eyayiphawula ilifa lensendo zikaBhenjamini emaceleni wonke.<verse eid="JOS 18:20"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOS 18:21"/>Isizwana sikaBhenjamini, usendo ngosendo sasilamadolobho alandelayo:</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 18:21">IJerikho, iBhethi-Hogla, i-Emeki Khezizi, <verse eid="JOS 18:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOS 18:22"/>iBhethi-Arabha, iZemarayimu, iBhetheli, <verse eid="JOS 18:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOS 18:23"/>i-Avimu, iPhara, i-Ofira, <verse eid="JOS 18:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOS 18:24"/>iKhefa-Amoni, i-Ofini leGebha, amadolobho alitshumi lambili kanye lemizana yawo.<verse eid="JOS 18:24"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOS 18:25"/>IGibhiyoni, iRama, iBherothi, <verse eid="JOS 18:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOS 18:26"/>iMizipha, iKhefira, iMoza, <verse eid="JOS 18:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOS 18:27"/>iRekhemu, i-Iphiyeli, iTharala, <verse eid="JOS 18:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOS 18:28"/>iZela, iHayelefi, idolobho lamaJebusi (okuyikuthi iJerusalema), iGibhiya leKhiriyathi, amadolobho alitshumi lane kanye lemizana yawo.</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="JOS 18:28">Leli kwakuyilifa likaBhenjamini lensendo zakhe.<verse eid="JOS 18:28"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 18"/>
  <chapter number="19" style="c" sid="JOS 19"/>
  <para style="s1">Isabelo SikaSimiyoni</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 19:1"/>Inkatho yesibili yawela esizwaneni sikaSimiyoni ngensendo zaso. Ilifa labo laliphakathi kwelizwe likaJuda. <verse eid="JOS 19:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 19:2"/>Laligoqela:</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 19:2">iBherishebha (noma Shebha), iMolada, <verse eid="JOS 19:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 19:3"/>iHazari-Shuwali, iBhala, i-Ezema, <verse eid="JOS 19:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 19:4"/>i-Elitholadi, iBhethuli, iHoma, <verse eid="JOS 19:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 19:5"/>iZikhilagi, iBhethi-Makhabhothi, iHazari-Susa, <verse eid="JOS 19:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 19:6"/>iBhethi-Lebhawothi leSharuheni, amadolobho alitshumi lantathu lemizana yawo;<verse eid="JOS 19:6"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 19:7"/>i-Ayini, iRimoni, i-Etheri le-Ashani, amadolobho amane lemizana yawo, <verse eid="JOS 19:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 19:8"/>layo yonke imizana eyakhelene lalawo madolobho kusiyafika eBhalathi-Bheri (iRama eseNegebi).</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="JOS 19:8">Leli kwakuyilifa lesizwana sikaSimiyoni ngensendo zaso. <verse eid="JOS 19:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 19:9"/>Ilifa labakoSimiyoni lathathwa kungxenye kaJuda ngenxa yokuthi isigaba sakoJuda sasisikhulu kakhulu. Ngakho abakoSimiyoni bathola ilifa labo phakathi kwelizwe lakoJuda.<verse eid="JOS 19:9"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isabelo SikaZebhuluni</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 19:10"/>Inkatho yesithathu yawela uZebhuluni lensendo zakhe:</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 19:10">Umngcele welifa labo wawufika eSaridi. <verse eid="JOS 19:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 19:11"/>Waqonda entshonalanga wadabula usiya eMarala, wathinta iDabheshethi, waqhela usiya odongeni eduze leJokhiniyamu. <verse eid="JOS 19:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 19:12"/>Wajikela empumalanga usuka eSaridi ukhangele empumalanga elizweni likaKhisilothi-Thabhori njalo waqhela usiya eDabherathi ukhwela usiya eJafiya. <verse eid="JOS 19:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 19:13"/>Waqhubeka ukhangele empumalanga usiya eGathi-Heferi le-Ethi Khazini; wathutshela eRimoni wasujikela eNeya. <verse eid="JOS 19:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 19:14"/>Lapho umngcele wabhoda enyakatho usiya eHanathoni wakhawula eSigodini se-Ifitha Eli.<verse eid="JOS 19:14"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 19:15"/>Kwakukhona njalo iKhathathi, iNahalali, iShimroni, i-Idala leBhethilehema. Kwakulamadolobho alitshumi lambili lemizana yawo.<verse eid="JOS 19:15"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOS 19:16"/>Amadolobho la lemizana yawo ayeyilifa likaZebhuluni lensendo.<verse eid="JOS 19:16"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isabelo Sika-Isakhari</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOS 19:17"/>Inkatho yesine yawela u-Isakhari ngensendo zakhe. <verse eid="JOS 19:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOS 19:18"/>Ilizwe labo laligoqela:</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 19:18">iJezerili, iKhesulothi, iShunemi, <verse eid="JOS 19:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOS 19:19"/>iHafarayimi, iShiyoni, i-Anaharathi, <verse eid="JOS 19:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOS 19:20"/>iRabhithi, iKhishiyoni, i-Ebhezi <verse eid="JOS 19:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOS 19:21"/>iRemethi, i-Eni-Ganimu, i-Eni-Hada leBhethi-Phazezi.<verse eid="JOS 19:21"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOS 19:22"/>Umngcele wawugudla iThabhori, iShahazuma leBhethi-Shemeshi wasukhawula eJodani.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 19:22">Kwakulamadolobho alitshumi lesithupha lemizana yawo.<verse eid="JOS 19:22"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOS 19:23"/>Amadolobho la lemizi yawo kwakuyilifa lesizwana sika-Isakhari lensendo zakhe.<verse eid="JOS 19:23"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isabelo Sika-Asheri</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOS 19:24"/>Inkatho yesihlanu yawela esizwaneni sika-Asheri ngensendo zakhe. <verse eid="JOS 19:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOS 19:25"/>Ilizwe labo laligoqela:</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 19:25">iHelikhathi, iHali, iBhetheni, i-Akhishafi, <verse eid="JOS 19:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOS 19:26"/>i-Alameleki, i-Amadi leMishali. Entshonalanga umngcele wagudla iKhameli leShihori-Libhinathi. <verse eid="JOS 19:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOS 19:27"/>Wajikela empumalanga ukhangele eBhethi-Dagoni, ugudla iZebhuluni leSigodi se-Ifitha Eli, waqonda enyakatho usiya eBhethi-Emekhi leNeyiyeli, usedlula eKhabhuli kwesenxele. <verse eid="JOS 19:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOS 19:28"/>Waya e-Abhidoni, eRehobhi, eHamoni leKhana usiyafika eSidoni enkulu. <verse eid="JOS 19:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOS 19:29"/>Umngcele waphinda wajika ukhangele eRama wasusiya edolobheni eliyinqaba eleThire, wajika ukhangele iHosa wathutshela olwandle olusesabelweni se-Akhizibhi, <verse eid="JOS 19:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="JOS 19:30"/>i-Uma, i-Afekhi leRehobhi.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 19:30">Kwakulamadolobho angamatshumi amabili lambili lemizana yawo.<verse eid="JOS 19:30"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="JOS 19:31"/>Amadolobho la lemizana yawo ayeyilifa lesizwana sika-Asheri lensendo zakhe.<verse eid="JOS 19:31"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isabelo SikaNafithali</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="JOS 19:32"/>Inkatho yesithupha yawela uNafithali ngensendo zakhe:<verse eid="JOS 19:32"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="JOS 19:33"/>Umgcele wasuka eHelefi kanye lesihlahla somʼOkhi eZananimi usedlula e-Adami Nekhebi leJabhiniyeli usiya eLakhumi njalo uphelela eJodani. <verse eid="JOS 19:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="JOS 19:34"/>Umngcele wadabula entshonalanga phakathi kwe-Azinothi-Thabhori wayaphuma ususeHukhokhi. Wagudla iZebhuluni eningizimu, i-Asheri entshonalanga kweJuda usiya empumalanga yeJodani.<verse eid="JOS 19:34"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="JOS 19:35"/>Amadolobho ayelezinqaba yiZidimu, iZeri, iHamathi, iRakhathi, iKhinerethi, <verse eid="JOS 19:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="JOS 19:36"/>i-Adama, iRama, iHazori, <verse eid="JOS 19:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="JOS 19:37"/>iKhedeshi, i-Edreyi, i-Eni-Hazo, <verse eid="JOS 19:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="JOS 19:38"/>iYironi, iMigidali-Eli, iHoremu, iBhethi-Anathi leBhethi-Shemeshi.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 19:38">Kwakulamadolobho alitshumi lesificamunwemunye lemizana yawo.<verse eid="JOS 19:38"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="JOS 19:39"/>Amadolobho la lemizana yawo kwakuyilifa lesizwana sikaNafithali ngensendo zakhe.<verse eid="JOS 19:39"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isabelo SikaDani</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="JOS 19:40"/>Inkatho yesikhombisa yawela isizwana sikaDani ngensendo zakhe. <verse eid="JOS 19:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="JOS 19:41"/>Ilizwe lelifa labo laligoqela:</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 19:41">iZora, i-Eshithawoli, i-Iri Shemeshi, <verse eid="JOS 19:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="JOS 19:42"/>iShayalabhini, i-Ayijaloni, i-Ithila, <verse eid="JOS 19:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="JOS 19:43"/>i-Eloni, iThimina, i-Ekroni, <verse eid="JOS 19:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="JOS 19:44"/>i-Elithekhe, iGibhethoni, iBhalathi, <verse eid="JOS 19:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="JOS 19:45"/>iJehudi, iBhene-Bherakhi, iGathi-Rimoni, <verse eid="JOS 19:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="JOS 19:46"/>iMe-Jarikhoni leRakhoni lendawo ekhangele iJopha.<verse eid="JOS 19:46"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="47" style="v" sid="JOS 19:47"/>(Kwathi abakoDani sebenqotshiwe bathathelwa ilizwe labo, basuka bayahlasela iLeshemu ngenkemba, bayithumba. Bahlala eLeshemu bayibiza ngokuthi yiDani, ibizo likakhokho wabo.)<verse eid="JOS 19:47"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="48" style="v" sid="JOS 19:48"/>Amadolobho la lemizana yawo ayeyilifa lesizwe sikaDani ngensendo zakhe.<verse eid="JOS 19:48"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isabelo SikaJoshuwa</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="49" style="v" sid="JOS 19:49"/>Bathi sebeqede ukwabelana umhlaba ngendlela eyayiphawulwe yinkatho, abako-Israyeli banika uJoshuwa indodana kaNuni ilifa phakathi kwabo, <verse eid="JOS 19:49"/><verse number="50" style="v" sid="JOS 19:50"/>njengokulaya <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>. Bamnika idolobho ayelicelile, iThimnathi-Sera elizweni lamaqaqa ko-Efrayimi. Wakha idolobho wahlala khona.<verse eid="JOS 19:50"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="51" style="v" sid="JOS 19:51"/>La yiwo amazwe u-Eliyazari umphristi, uJoshuwa indodana kaNuni labakhokheli bonke lensendo zezizwana zako-Israyeli abazehlukanisela wona ngenkatho eShilo phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> entubeni yethente lokuhlangana. Ngakho-ke baqeda ukwaba umhlaba.<verse eid="JOS 19:51"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 19"/>
  <chapter number="20" style="c" sid="JOS 20"/>
  <para style="s1">Amadolobho Okuphephela</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 20:1"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuJoshuwa: <verse eid="JOS 20:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 20:2"/>“Tshela abako-Israyeli ukuthi baphawule amadolobho okuphephela njengokulilaya engakwenza ngoMosi, <verse eid="JOS 20:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 20:3"/>ukuze wonke umuntu obulala omunye ngengozi hatshi ngabomo abalekele kulo ukuze aphephe esandleni somphindiseli wegazi. <verse eid="JOS 20:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 20:4"/>Lapho ebalekela kwelinye lala amadolobho, kumele eme esangweni ledolobho abesesitsho ukuthi ukhala ngani ebadaleni balelodolobho. Abadala sebezamamukela-ke edolobheni labo besebemnika indawo yokuhlala phakathi kwabo. <verse eid="JOS 20:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 20:5"/>Nxa umphindiseli wegazi emlandela, akumelanga bamnikele lowo owetheswa umlandu ngoba kambulalanga ngabomo kumbe ngenhliziyo embi. <verse eid="JOS 20:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 20:6"/>Usezahlala kulelodolobho kuze kufike isikhathi sokuthonisiswa phambi kwebandla njalo kuze kufe umphristi omkhulu oyabe ephethe umsebenzi ngalesosikhathi. Lapho usengabuyela ngakibo, edolobheni abaleka kulo.”<verse eid="JOS 20:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 20:7"/>Ngakho behlukanisa iKhedeshi eseGalile elizweni lamaqaqa koNafithali, iShekhemu elizweni lamaqaqa ko-Efrayimi leKhiriyathi Aribha (okutsho iHebhroni) elizweni lamaqaqa koJuda. <verse eid="JOS 20:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 20:8"/>Empumalanga yeJodani leJerikho baphawula iBhezeri enkangala esemagcekeni esizwaneni sikaRubheni, iRamothi eseGiliyadi esizwaneni sikaGadi, leGolani eseBhashani esizwaneni sikaManase. <verse eid="JOS 20:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 20:9"/>Iloba ngubani owako-Israyeli kumbe omunye owezizweni ohlala phakathi kwabo owabulala omunye umuntu ngengozi wayengabalekela emadolobheni aqanjiweyo, aphephe ekubulaweni ngumphindiseli wegazi engakamiswa phambi kwebandla ukuba athonisiswe.<verse eid="JOS 20:9"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 20"/>
  <chapter number="21" style="c" sid="JOS 21"/>
  <para style="s1">Amadolobho AbaLevi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 21:1"/>Abakhokheli bezimuli zabaLevi balanda u-Eliyazari umphristi, uJoshuwa indodana kaNuni, labakhokheli bezinye izimuli ezizwaneni zako-Israyeli <verse eid="JOS 21:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 21:2"/>eShilo eseKhenani bathi kubo, “<char style="nd">UThixo</char> walaya ngoMosi wathi lisinike amadolobho okuhlala, alamadlelo ezifuyo zethu.”<verse eid="JOS 21:2"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 21:3"/>Ngakho njengoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wayelayile, abako-Israyeli banika abaLevi amadolobho alandelayo lamadlelo kuvela elifeni labo:<verse eid="JOS 21:3"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 21:4"/>Inkatho yakuqala yawela amaKhohathi ngensendo zawo. AbaLevi ababeyizizukulwane zika-Aroni umphristi babelwa amadolobho alitshumi lantathu ezizwaneni zakoJuda, ezakoSimiyoni lezakoBhenjamini.<verse eid="JOS 21:4"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 21:5"/>Izizukulwane zonke zikaKhohathi zabelwa amadolobho alitshumi kuzinsendo zezizwana zako-Efrayimi, ezakoDani lengxenye yakoManase.<verse eid="JOS 21:5"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 21:6"/>Izizukulwane zikaGeshoni zabelwa amadolobho alitshumi lantathu kuzinsendo zezizwana zako-Isakhari, ezako-Asheri, ezakoNafithali lengxenye yesizwana sakoManase eBhashani.<verse eid="JOS 21:6"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 21:7"/>Izizukulwane zikaMerari ngensendo zazo zathola amadolobho alitshumi lambili ezizwaneni zakoRubheni, ezakoGadi lezakoZebhuluni.<verse eid="JOS 21:7"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 21:8"/>Ngakho abako-Israyeli babela abaLevi amadolobho la lamadlelo awo, njengokulaya <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> ngoMosi.<verse eid="JOS 21:8"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 21:9"/>Ezizwaneni zakoJuda lezakoSimiyoni amadolobho abiwayo nanka ngamabizo awo <verse eid="JOS 21:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 21:10"/>Amadolobho la anikwa izizukulwane zika-Aroni ezazivela kuzinsendo zamaKhohathi phakathi kwabaLevi ngoba inkatho yakuqala yawela kuzo:<verse eid="JOS 21:10"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 21:11"/>Bazinika iKhiriyathi Aribha (okutsho iHebhroni) emadlelweni akulowomango elizweni lamaqaqa koJuda (u-Abha wayengukhokho ka-Anakhi). <verse eid="JOS 21:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 21:12"/>Kodwa amasimu lemizana okwakuseduzane ledolobho babekunike uKhalebi indodana kaJefune ukuba kube ngokwakhe. <verse eid="JOS 21:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 21:13"/>Ngakho izizukulwane zika-Aroni umphristi bazinika iHebhroni (idolobho lokuphephela kwalabo abalamacala okubulala), iLibhina, <verse eid="JOS 21:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 21:14"/>iJathiri, i-Eshithemowa <verse eid="JOS 21:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 21:15"/>iHoloni, iDebhiri, <verse eid="JOS 21:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOS 21:16"/>i-Ayini, iJutha leBhethi-Shemeshi, ndawonye lamadlelo awo, amadolobho ayisificamunwemunye esuka ezizwaneni lezi zombili.<verse eid="JOS 21:16"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOS 21:17"/>Esizweni sakoBhenjamini bazinika</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="JOS 21:17">iGibhiyoni, iGebha, <verse eid="JOS 21:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOS 21:18"/>i-Anathothi le-Alimoni, ndawonye lamadlelo awo kwaba ngamadolobho amane.<verse eid="JOS 21:18"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOS 21:19"/>Wonke amadolobho abaphristi, izizukulwane zika-Aroni, ayelitshumi lantathu ndawonye lamadlelo awo.<verse eid="JOS 21:19"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOS 21:20"/>Ezinye zonke insendo zikaKhohathi phakathi kwabaLevi zabelwa amadolobho esizwaneni sako-Efrayimi.<verse eid="JOS 21:20"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOS 21:21"/>Elizweni elilamaqaqa ko-Efrayimi zanikwa</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="JOS 21:21">iShekhemu (idolobho lokuphephela kwalabo abalamacala okubulala) leGezeri, <verse eid="JOS 21:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOS 21:22"/>iKhibhizayimi leBhethi-Horoni, ndawonye lamadlelo awo, kwaba ngamadolobho amane.<verse eid="JOS 21:22"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOS 21:23"/>Esizwaneni sakoDani zathola,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="JOS 21:23">i-Elithekhe, iGibhethoni, <verse eid="JOS 21:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOS 21:24"/>i-Ayijaloni leGathi-Rimoni, ndawonye lamadlelo awo, kwaba ngamadolobho amane.<verse eid="JOS 21:24"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOS 21:25"/>Kungxenye yesizwe sakoManase zathola</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="JOS 21:25">iThanakhi leGathi-Rimoni, ndawonye lamadlelo awo, kwakungamadolobho amabili.<verse eid="JOS 21:25"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOS 21:26"/>Wonke la amadolobho alitshumi lamadlelo awo anikwa kuzozonke insendo zamaKhohathi.<verse eid="JOS 21:26"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOS 21:27"/>Insendo zamaLevi ezeGeshoni zanikwa:</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 21:27">kungxenye yesizwana sakoManase,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="JOS 21:27">iGolani eseBhashani (idolobho lokuphephela kwalabo abalamacala okubulala) leBheshithera, ndawonye lamadlelo awo, amadolobho amabili;<verse eid="JOS 21:27"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOS 21:28"/>esizwaneni sika-Isakhari,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="JOS 21:28">iKhishiyoni, iDabherathi, <verse eid="JOS 21:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOS 21:29"/>iJamuthi le-Eni-Ganimu, ndawonye lamadlelo awo, amadolobho amane;<verse eid="JOS 21:29"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="JOS 21:30"/>esizwaneni sika-Asheri,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="JOS 21:30">iMishali, i-Abhidoni, <verse eid="JOS 21:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="JOS 21:31"/>iHelikhathi leRehobhi, ndawonye lamadlelo awo, amadolobho amane;<verse eid="JOS 21:31"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="JOS 21:32"/>kusukela esizwaneni sakoNafithali,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="JOS 21:32">iKhedeshi eseGalile (idolobho lokuphephela kwalabo abalamacala okubulala), iHamothi-Dori leKhathani, ndawonye lamadlelo awo, amadolobho amathathu.<verse eid="JOS 21:32"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="JOS 21:33"/>Wonke amadolobho ensendo zamaGeshoni ayelitshumi lantathu, ndawonye lamadlelo awo.<verse eid="JOS 21:33"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="JOS 21:34"/>Insendo zamaMerari (okutsho bonke abaLevi) zanikwa kanje</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="JOS 21:34">esizwaneni sikaZebhuluni,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="JOS 21:34">iJokhiniyamu, iKhatha, <verse eid="JOS 21:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="JOS 21:35"/>iDimina leNahalali ndawonye lamadlelo awo, amadolobho amane.<verse eid="JOS 21:35"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="JOS 21:36"/>Esizwaneni sakoRubheni,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="JOS 21:36">iBhezeri, iJahazi, <verse eid="JOS 21:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="JOS 21:37"/>iKhedemothi leMefahathi ndawonye lamadlelo awo, amadolobho amane.<verse eid="JOS 21:37"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="JOS 21:38"/>Esizwaneni sakoGadi,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="JOS 21:38">iRamothi eseGiliyadi (idolobho lokuphephela kwalabo abalamacala okubulala), iMahanayimi, <verse eid="JOS 21:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="JOS 21:39"/>iHeshibhoni leJazeri ndawonye lamadlelo awo, amadolobho amane esewonke.<verse eid="JOS 21:39"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="JOS 21:40"/>Wonke amadolobho abelwa insendo zamaMerari, eyingxenye yonke eseleyo yabaLevi, ayelitshumi lambili.<verse eid="JOS 21:40"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="JOS 21:41"/>Amadolobho abaLevi elizweni eliphansi kwabako-Israyeli ayengamatshumi amane lasificaminwembili mibili esewonke ndawonye lamadlelo awo. <verse eid="JOS 21:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="JOS 21:42"/>Linye ngalinye lamadolobho la lalilamadlelo aligombolozeleyo. Konke kwakunjalo ngawo wonke la amadolobho.<verse eid="JOS 21:42"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="JOS 21:43"/>Ngakho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wanika abako-Israyeli wonke umhlaba ayefunge ukuwunika okhokho babo, bawuthatha bakha khonapho. <verse eid="JOS 21:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="JOS 21:44"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> wabapha ukuphumula enhlangothini zonke, njengokufunga ayekwenze kubokhokho babo. Akulasitha lesisodwa esenelisa ukumelana labo; <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wanikela zonke izitha zabo kubo. <verse eid="JOS 21:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="JOS 21:45"/>Asikho lesisodwa sazo zonke izithembiso ezinhle <char style="nd">zikaThixo</char> endlini ka-Israyeli esingagcwalisekanga; zonke zagcwaliseka.<verse eid="JOS 21:45"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 21"/>
  <chapter number="22" style="c" sid="JOS 22"/>
  <para style="s1">Izizwana ZeMpumalanga Ziphindela Ekhaya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 22:1"/>UJoshuwa wamema abakoRubheni, abakoGadi lengxenye yesizwe sikaManase <verse eid="JOS 22:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 22:2"/>wathi kubo, “Selenze konke uMosi inceku <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> eyakulayayo, njalo lingilalele kukho konke engililaye ngakho. <verse eid="JOS 22:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 22:3"/>Okwesikhathi eside khathesi, kuze kube lamuhla, kalizange lihlamukele abafowenu kodwa lenze umsebenzi lowo <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu alinike wona. <verse eid="JOS 22:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 22:4"/>Njengoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu wanika abafowenu ukuphumula njengokuthembisa kwakhe, buyelani emakhaya enu elizweni uMosi inceku <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> alinika lona ngaphetsheya kweJodani. <verse eid="JOS 22:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 22:5"/>Kodwa linanzelele kakhulu ukuthi lilondoloza umlayo lomthetho uMosi inceku <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> alinika wona: Ukuthanda <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu, ukuhamba ezindleleni zakhe zonke, ukulalela imilayo yakhe, ukubambelela kuye lokumsebenzela ngenhliziyo yenu yonke lomphefumulo wenu wonke.”<verse eid="JOS 22:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 22:6"/>UJoshuwa wasebabusisa wathi kabahambe; yikho basebesiya emizini yabo. <verse eid="JOS 22:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 22:7"/>Ingxenye yesizwana sakoManase uMosi wayeyinike ilizwe eBhashani, kwathi eyinye ingxenye yesizwana uJoshuwa wayeyinike indawo lapho okwakwakhele abafowabo eJodani. Kwathi uJoshuwa esethe kabahambe emakhaya, wababusisa <verse eid="JOS 22:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 22:8"/>wathi, “Buyelani emakhaya enu lenotho yenu enengi, lilemihlambi emikhulu yezifuyo, lilesiliva, igolide ithusi lensimbi, lamalembu amanengi, beselisabelana labafowenu lokho elakuthumba ezitheni zenu.”<verse eid="JOS 22:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 22:9"/>Ngakho abakoRubheni, abakoGadi lengxenye yesizwana sakoManase batshiya abako-Israyeli eShilo eseKhenani babuyela eGiliyadi, ilizwe labo, ababelizuze kulandela umlayo <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> awethula ngoMosi.<verse eid="JOS 22:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 22:10"/>Bathi sebefike eGelithothi eduzane leJodani elizweni leKhenani, abakoRubheni, abakoGadi lengxenye yesizwana sakoManase bakha i-alithari elikhulu eduzane leJodani. <verse eid="JOS 22:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 22:11"/>Kwathi abako-Israyeli sebezwe ukuthi sebakhe i-alithari emngceleni weKhenani eGelithothi duzane leJodani eceleni lako-Israyeli, <verse eid="JOS 22:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 22:12"/>umphakathi wonke wako-Israyeli wabuthana eShilo ukulungiselela ukulwa labo empini.<verse eid="JOS 22:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 22:13"/>Ngakho abako-Israyeli bathuma uFinehasi indodana ka-Eliyazari, umphristi elizweni leGiliyadi kuRubheni, uGadi lengxenye yesizwana sakoManase. <verse eid="JOS 22:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 22:14"/>Waphelekezelwa zinduna ezilitshumi, inye ngayinye ivela phakathi kwezizwe zonke zako-Israyeli njalo iyinhloko yesigaba semuli yensendo zako-Israyeli.<verse eid="JOS 22:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 22:15"/>Ekuyeni kwabo eGiliyadi, kuRubheni loGadi lengxenye yesizwana sakoManase bathi kubo: <verse eid="JOS 22:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOS 22:16"/>“Umphakathi wonke <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> uthi: ‘Kungani lisuke langathembeki kuNkulunkulu wako-Israyeli ngale indlela? Kungani lilahle uNkulunkulu lizakhela i-alithari njengokumhlamukela khathesi. <verse eid="JOS 22:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOS 22:17"/>Kambe ukona kukaPheyori kakwanelanga kithi na? Kuze kube lamhla kasikazihlambululi esonweni leso, lanxa umkhuhlane wake wahlasela isizwe <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char>! <verse eid="JOS 22:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOS 22:18"/>Selibalekela <char style="nd">uThixo</char> na?</para>
  <para style="p" vid="JOS 22:18">Nxa lingahlamukela <char style="nd">uThixo</char> lamhla, kusasa uzazondela isizwe sonke sako-Israyeli: <verse eid="JOS 22:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOS 22:19"/>Nxa umhlaba elilawo ungcolisiwe wozani emhlabeni <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> lapho ithabanikeli <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> elimi khona beselisabelana umhlaba lathi. Kodwa lingahlamukeli <char style="nd">uThixo</char> kumbe thina ngokuzakhela i-alithari lenu, ngaphandle kwe-alithari <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wethu. <verse eid="JOS 22:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOS 22:20"/>Lapho u-Akhani indodana kaZera aze angathembeki ezintweni ezingcwelisiweyo, isijeziso kasehlelanga isizwe sonke sako-Israyeli yini? Kayisuye yedwa owafela isono sakhe.’ ”<verse eid="JOS 22:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOS 22:21"/>Ngakho uRubheni, uGadi lengxenye yesizwe sakoManase baphendula abakhokheli bezinsendo zako-Israyeli bathi: <verse eid="JOS 22:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOS 22:22"/>“USomandla, uNkulunkulu <char style="nd">uThixo</char>! USomandla uNkulunkulu <char style="nd">uThixo</char>! Uyazi! Njalo u-Israyeli kabe lolwazi! Nxa lokhu bekuyikuhlamukela kumbe ukuqholozela <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, lingasisindisi lamhlanje. <verse eid="JOS 22:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOS 22:23"/>Nxa sazakhela i-alithari lethu ukwenzela ukubalekela <char style="nd">uThixo</char> lokunikela ngeminikelo yokutshiswa leminikelo yamabele, kumbe ukunikela ngeminikelo yokuthula kulo, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ngokwakhe kasijezise.<verse eid="JOS 22:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOS 22:24"/>Hatshi! Sakwenza sisesaba ukuthi kwelinye ilanga izizukulwane zenu zingathi kwezethu, ‘Lilani <char style="nd">loThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu wako-Israyeli? <verse eid="JOS 22:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOS 22:25"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> sewenza iJodani ibe ngumngcele phakathi kwethu lani lina maRubheni lamaGadi! Kalilasabelo <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>.’ Ngakho izizukulwane zenu zingenza ukuthi ezethu ziyekele ukwesaba <char style="nd">uThixo</char>.<verse eid="JOS 22:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOS 22:26"/>Yikho sathi, ‘Kasilungiseni sakhe i-alithari, kodwa hatshi eleminikelo yokutshiswa kumbe imihlatshelo.’ <verse eid="JOS 22:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOS 22:27"/>Ngeyinye indlela, kuzakuba yibufakazi phakathi kwethu lani lezizukulwane ezizalandela, ukuthi sizekhonza <char style="nd">uThixo</char> endlini yakhe engcwele ngeminikelo yokutshiswa, iminikelo yethu kanye leyokuthula. Ngakho kwelakusasa izizukulwane zenu kazisoze zithi kwezethu, ‘Kalilasabelo <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>.’<verse eid="JOS 22:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOS 22:28"/>Njalo sathi, ‘Bangavele batsho lokhu kithi kumbe kuzizukulwane zethu, sizaphendula sithi: Khangelani emfanekisweni we-alithari <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>, elakhiwa ngobaba, hatshi eleminikelo yokutshiswa lemihlatshelo, kodwa njengobufakazi phakathi kwethu lani.’<verse eid="JOS 22:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOS 22:29"/>Kukhatshana kithi ukuthi sihlamukele <char style="nd">uThixo</char> simfulathele lamhla ngokwakha i-alithari leminikelo yokutshiswa, iminikelo yamabele lemihlatshelo, ngaphandle kwe-alithari <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wethu elimi phambi kwethabanikeli lakhe.”<verse eid="JOS 22:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="JOS 22:30"/>Kwathi uFinehasi umphristi labakhokheli besizwe, abakhokheli bezinsendo zako-Israyeli, sebezwe okwakutshiwo nguRubheni, uGadi loManase bathokoza. <verse eid="JOS 22:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="JOS 22:31"/>UFinehasi indodana ka-Eliyazari, umphristi, wathi kuRubheni, uGadi loManase, “Lamhla siyazi ukuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ulathi, ngenxa yokuthi kalizange liyekele ukwethembeka phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> kuloludaba. Khathesi selihlenge abako-Israyeli esandleni <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char>.”<verse eid="JOS 22:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="JOS 22:32"/>UFinehasi indodana ka-Eliyazari, umphristi, labakhokheli babuyela eKhenani bevela emhlanganweni wabo labakoRubheni labakoGadi eGiliyadi basebebika kwabako-Israyeli. <verse eid="JOS 22:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="JOS 22:33"/>Bathokoza ukuzwa umbiko basebedumisa uNkulunkulu. Kabasakhulumanga njalo ngokuya empini yokubalwisa ukwenzela ukutshabalalisa ilizwe lapho abakoRubheni labakoGadi ababehlala khona.<verse eid="JOS 22:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="JOS 22:34"/>Njalo abakoRubheni labakoGadi banika i-alithari lelibizo: UBufakazi Phakathi Kwethu ukuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> unguNkulunkulu.<verse eid="JOS 22:34"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 22"/>
  <chapter number="23" style="c" sid="JOS 23"/>
  <para style="s1">UJoshuwa Uvalelisa Abakhokheli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 23:1"/>Ngemva kwesikhathi eside njalo <char style="nd">uThixo</char> esephumuze abako-Israyeli kuzozonke izitha zabo ezazibagombolozele, uJoshuwa ngalesosikhathi esekhulile eseleminyaka eminengi, <verse eid="JOS 23:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 23:2"/>wabiza bonke abako-Israyeli, abadala babo, abakhokheli babo, abahluleli babo leziphathamandla zabo wathi kubo: “Sengimdala njalo sengiluphele kakhulu. <verse eid="JOS 23:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 23:3"/>Lina ngokwenu selikubonile konke lokho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu akwenzileyo kuzozonke lezi izizwe esenzela lina; <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu owalilwelayo. <verse eid="JOS 23:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 23:4"/>Khumbulani ukuthi ngalabela njani ukuba kube yilifa lenu lezizwana zenu wonke umhlaba wezizwe ezasalayo, izizwe engazinqobayo, phakathi kweJodani loLwandle Olukhulu entshonalanga. <verse eid="JOS 23:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 23:5"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu ngokwakhe uzabaxotsha endleleni yenu. Uzabasusa lina lingakafiki, njalo lina lizathatha umhlaba wabo, njengokuthembisa <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu.<verse eid="JOS 23:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 23:6"/>Qinani kakhulu; linanzelele ukuthi lilalela konke okulotshwe eGwalweni lwemiThetho kaMosi, lingaphambukelanga kwesokudla kumbe esenxele. <verse eid="JOS 23:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 23:7"/>Lingaze lazisondeza ezizweni lezi eziphakathi kwenu; lingaze labiza amagama abonkulunkulu bazo kumbe lifunge ngabo. Akumelanga ukuthi libasebenzele lokubakhothamela. <verse eid="JOS 23:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 23:8"/>Kodwa kumele libambelele <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu njengalokhu eselikwenze kwaze kwaba khathesi.<verse eid="JOS 23:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 23:9"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> usezixotshile phambi kwenu izizwe ezilamandla; kuze kube lamhla kakho owenelisa ukumelana lani. <verse eid="JOS 23:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 23:10"/>Oyedwa wenu uyenelisa ukwehlula abantu abayinkulungwane eyodwa ngenxa yokuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu uyalilwela njengokuthembisa kwakhe. <verse eid="JOS 23:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 23:11"/>Ngakho-ke nanzelelani ukuthi liyamthanda <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu.<verse eid="JOS 23:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 23:12"/>Kodwa lingabaleka beselisiba lobungane lalabo abasindileyo phakathi kwezizwe lezi ezizasala phakathi kwenu njalo lingavumelana lokuthathana lokudlelana lazo, <verse eid="JOS 23:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 23:13"/>lapho lingaba leqiniso lokuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu kasoze azixotshe izizwe phambi kwenu. Kodwa-ke zizakuba yimijibila lezithiyo kini, zizakuba yiziswebhu emihlane yenu lameva emehlweni enu, lize libhujiswe elizweni leli elihle <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu alinika lona.<verse eid="JOS 23:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 23:14"/>Khathesi sengizahamba ngendlela yomhlaba wonke. Liyazi ngezinhliziyo zenu lemiphefumulo ukuthi kasikho isithembiso lasinye esihle phakathi kwalezo elazinikwa <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu esehlulekayo. Zonke izithembiso sezagcwaliswa; kasikho lesisodwa esehlulekayo. <verse eid="JOS 23:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 23:15"/>Kodwa njengoba zonke izithembiso ezinhle <char style="nd">zikaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu seziphumelele, kunjalo <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uzalilethela bonke ububi alethusela ngabo, aze alibhubhise elizweni leli elihle alinike lona. <verse eid="JOS 23:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOS 23:16"/>Lingephula isivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu, owalilayayo ngaso liyokhonza abanye onkulunkulu libakhothamele, ulaka <char style="nd">lukaThixo</char> luzavutha kini, njalo lizabhubha ngokuphangisa elizweni elihle alinike lona.”<verse eid="JOS 23:16"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 23"/>
  <chapter number="24" style="c" sid="JOS 24"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukuvuselelwa Kwesivumelwano EShekhemu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JOS 24:1"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa wabuthanisa zonke izizwana zako-Israyeli eShekhemu. Wamema bonke abadala, abakhokheli, abahluleli leziphathamandla zako-Israyeli, njalo bazethula phambi kukaNkulunkulu.<verse eid="JOS 24:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOS 24:2"/>UJoshuwa wathi ebantwini bonke, “<char style="nd">UThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu wako-Israyeli uthi: ‘Kudala okhokho benu, okugoqela uThera uyise ka-Abhrahama loNahori, babehlala ngaphetsheya koMfula njalo bekhonza abanye onkulunkulu. <verse eid="JOS 24:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="JOS 24:3"/>Kodwa ngathatha uyihlo u-Abhrahama elizweni elingaphetsheya koMfula ngamkhokhelela eKhenani ngamnika izizukulwane ezinengi. Ngamnika u-Isaka, <verse eid="JOS 24:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOS 24:4"/>njalo u-Isaka ngamnika uJakhobe lo-Esawu. Nganika ilizwe lonke elilamaqaqa eleSeyiri ku-Esawu, kodwa uJakhobe lamadodana akhe baya eGibhithe.<verse eid="JOS 24:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="JOS 24:5"/>Ngasengithuma uMosi lo-Aroni, njalo ngajezisa amaGibhithe ngalokho engakwenza khonale ngasengilikhupha khona. <verse eid="JOS 24:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOS 24:6"/>Ekukhupheni kwami okhokho benu eGibhithe, beza olwandle njalo amaGibhithe axotshana labo ngezinqola lamabhiza baze bayafika eLwandle Olubomvu. <verse eid="JOS 24:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOS 24:7"/>Kodwa bakhala <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> befuna uncedo yena waseletha umnyama phakathi kwenu lamaGibhithe; waletha ulwandle phezu kwabo wabembesa ngalo. Lazibonela ngamehlo enu lokho engakwenza kumaGibhithe. Laselihlala enkangala okwesikhathi eside.<verse eid="JOS 24:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="JOS 24:8"/>Ngaliletha elizweni lama-Amori ayehlala empumalanga yeJodani. Balwisana lani, kodwa mina ngabanikela ezandleni zenu. Ngababhubhisa phambi kwenu njalo laselithatha ilizwe labo. <verse eid="JOS 24:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="JOS 24:9"/>Lapho uBhalaki indodana kaZiphori inkosi yaseMowabi, alungiselela ukulwisana lo-Israyeli, wathumela uBhalamu indodana kaBheyori ukuthi aliqalekise. <verse eid="JOS 24:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="JOS 24:10"/>Kodwa ngala ukulalela uBhalamu, ngakho walibusisa njalonjalo mina ngasengilihlenga esandleni sakhe.<verse eid="JOS 24:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOS 24:11"/>Laselichapha uJodani leza eJerikho. Izakhamizi zeJerikho zalwisana lani njengalokho okwenziwa ngama-Amori, amaPherizi, amaKhenani, amaHithi, amaGigashi, amaHivi lamaJebusi, kodwa ngabanikela ezandleni zenu. <verse eid="JOS 24:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOS 24:12"/>Ngathumela olonyovu phambi kwenu, olwabaxotsha phambi kwenu kanye lamakhosi amabili ama-Amori. Kalizange likwenze ngenkemba yenu langedandili lenu. <verse eid="JOS 24:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOS 24:13"/>Ngakho ngalinika ilizwe elingazanga liliginqele lamadolobho elingazange liwakhe; njalo lihlala phakathi kwawo njalo lisidla ezivinini zama-oliva elingazihlanyelanga.’<verse eid="JOS 24:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOS 24:14"/>Ngakho mesabeni <char style="nd">uThixo</char> limkhonze ngokuthembeka konke. Lahlani onkulunkulu ababekhonzwa ngokhokho benu ngaphetsheya koMfula laseGibhithe, likhonze <char style="nd">uThixo</char>. <verse eid="JOS 24:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="JOS 24:15"/>Kodwa nxa ukukhonza <char style="nd">uThixo</char> kukhanya kungathandeki kini, khethani phakathi kwenu namhlanje lowo elizamkhonza, kumbe ngonkulunkulu okhokho benu ababebakhonza ngaphetsheya koMfula kumbe onkulunkulu bama-Amori, lawo elihlala elizweni lawo. Kodwa mina lendlu yami sizakhonza <char style="nd">uThixo</char>.”<verse eid="JOS 24:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="JOS 24:16"/>Abantu basebephendula besithi, “Akube khatshana lathi ukuthi silahle <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ukuze sikhonze abanye onkulunkulu! <verse eid="JOS 24:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOS 24:17"/><char style="nd">KwakunguThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wethu ngokwakhe owasikhuphayo thina kanye labobaba eGibhithe sisuka elizweni lobugqili, wasesenza izimanga ezinkulu emehlweni ethu. Wasivikela kulolonke uhambo lwethu lakuzo zonke izizwe. <verse eid="JOS 24:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOS 24:18"/>Njalo <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wazixotsha phambi kwethu zonke izizwe, okugoqela ama-Amori ayehlala elizweni. Lathi sizamkhonza <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ngoba unguNkulunkulu wethu.”<verse eid="JOS 24:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOS 24:19"/>UJoshuwa wathi ebantwini, “Kalenelisi ukumkhonza <char style="nd">uThixo</char>. UnguNkulunkulu ongcwele; unguNkulunkulu olobukhwele. Kasoze alixolele ekuhlamukeni kwenu lezonweni zenu. <verse eid="JOS 24:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOS 24:20"/>Nxa lingatshiya <char style="nd">uThixo</char> beselikhonza abanye onkulunkulu bezizweni uzaliphendukela alehlisele umonakalo aliqede du, yena ubelungile.”<verse eid="JOS 24:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="JOS 24:21"/>Kodwa abantu bathi kuJoshuwa, “Hatshi! Sizamkhonza <char style="nd">uThixo</char>.”<verse eid="JOS 24:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOS 24:22"/>UJoshuwa wathi, “Yini elizifakazelayo ukuthi selikhethe ukukhonza <char style="nd">uThixo</char>.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="JOS 24:22">” Baphendula bathi, “Yebo singofakazi.”<verse eid="JOS 24:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="JOS 24:23"/>UJoshuwa wathi kubo, “Ngakho-ke lahlani bonke onkulunkulu bezizweni abaphakathi kwenu beselinikela inhliziyo zenu <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu wako-Israyeli.”<verse eid="JOS 24:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOS 24:24"/>Abantu bathi kuJoshuwa, “Sizamkhonza <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wethu simlalele.”<verse eid="JOS 24:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOS 24:25"/>Ngalelolanga uJoshuwa wenzela abantu isivumelwano, njalo wabenzela imithetho lemilayo khonapho eShekhemu. <verse eid="JOS 24:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="JOS 24:26"/>UJoshuwa waloba konke lokhu oGwalweni lwemiThetho kaNkulunkulu. Wasethatha ilitshe elikhulu walimisa phansi kwesihlahla somʼOkhi eduzane lendawo engcwele <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>.<verse eid="JOS 24:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="JOS 24:27"/>Wathi ebantwini bonke, “Khangelani! Ilitshe leli lizakuba yibufakazi kithi sonke. Selizwile wonke amazwi akhulunywe <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> kithi. Lizakuba ngofakazi wokulilahla nxa lingakhulumi iqiniso kuNkulunkulu.”<verse eid="JOS 24:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="JOS 24:28"/>UJoshuwa wasetshela abantu ukuba bahambe, yilowo esiya elifeni lakhe.<verse eid="JOS 24:28"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ungcwatshelwa Elizweni Lesithembiso</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="JOS 24:29"/>Ngemva kwezinto lezi, uJoshuwa indodana kaNuni, inceku <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> wafa eseleminyaka elikhulu letshumi. <verse eid="JOS 24:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="JOS 24:30"/>Njalo bamngcwaba elizweni alizuza njengelifa, eThimnathi-Sera elizweni elilamaqaqa elako-Efrayimi enyakatho yentaba yeGashi.<verse eid="JOS 24:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="JOS 24:31"/>Abako-Israyeli bamkhonza <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ngezinsuku zokuphila kukaJoshuwa labadala kulaye ababesele bephila njalo bebone zonke izinto <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ayezenzele abako-Israyeli.<verse eid="JOS 24:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="JOS 24:32"/>Njalo amathambo kaJosefa, abako-Israyeli ababesuke lawo eGibhithe, angcwatshelwa eShekhemu esiqintini somhlaba leso uJakhobe asithenga ngenhlamvu ezilikhulu zesiliva emadodaneni kaHamori, uyise kaShekhemu. Leli laba yilifa lezizukulwane zikaJosefa.<verse eid="JOS 24:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="JOS 24:33"/>U-Eliyazari indodana ka-Aroni wafa wasengcwatshelwa eGibhiya, eyayabelwe indodana yakhe uFinehasi elizweni lamaqaqa elako-Efrayimi.<verse eid="JOS 24:33"/></para>
  <chapter eid="JOS 24"/>
</usx>
